Kotu ta cinna wuta a lokacin zanga-zanga a California
OAKLAND, Ca. - Masu zanga-zanga a California sun cinna wuta a gidan kotu, sun lalata ofishin 'yan sanda da kuma kai hari ga jami'ai bayan zanga-zangar lumana ta kara tsanani a ranar Asabar, in ji 'yan sanda na Oakland.
Masu zanga-zangar sun fasa tagogi, sun fesa fentin rubutu, sun harba kayan wuta da kuma lasisi mai nisa a jami'an, in ji sashen Oakland a Twitter.
Yawancin tweets sun yi kira ga zaman lafiya kuma sun nemi masu shiryawa da su "taimaka mana samar da wurare masu aminci da wurare masu aminci ga masu zanga-zanga."
An fara zanga-zangar ne da yammacin ranar Asabar tare da kungiyoyi irin su "Wall of Moms", kama daga kungiyar da ta kafa a Portland, Oregon, yayin da masu zanga-zangar suka fuskanci suka tare da jami'an Amurka da aka tura zuwa wannan birnin don tsare wani gidan kotun tarayya.
Shugaba Donald Trump ya tura jami'an gwamnatin tarayya domin su matsa kaimi kan zanga-zangar da ta faru cikin dare tun bayan mutuwar George Floyd a Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga watan Mayu.
Zanga-zangar a Oakland ta soma ne cikin lumana, amma ta rikide ta koma tashin hankali har cikin dare.
'Yan sanda sun kaddamar da wani "taro ba bisa ka'ida ba" da misalin karfe 11:30 na yamma kuma jami'ai sun nemi jama'a su tarwatse.
Wutar ta tashi ne a babbar kotun da ke yankin Alameda kuma ba da jimawa ba, kamar yadda kafar yada labarai ta ruwaito.
'Yan sanda sun ce masu zanga-zangar a wani lokaci suna "watse tagogi da kuma kiran wariyar launin fata a mazauna."
Hotunan da sashen ya wallafa sun nuna gilashin da ya fashe da fenti a wani ginin 'yan sanda.
Kasancewar tsaro sosai a wajen ofishin jakadancin Amurka a birnin Chengdu na kasar Sin
An samu matsanancin tsaro a wajen ofishin jakadancin Amurka da ke birnin Chengdu na kasar Sin a ranar Lahadi, yayin da ma'aikatan Amurka suka shirya barin wurin.
An ga manyan motoci uku masu motsi sun shiga cikin fili na ginin, yayin da 'yan sanda masu dauke da kayan kwalliya da kayan kwalliya suka yi layi a dukkanin bangarorin titin, wadanda aka lissafa su da shingayen karfe.
Editan jaridar Global Times na kasar Sin ya bayyana cewa, an bai wa ofishin jakadancin Amurka da ke Chengdu sa'o'i 72 don rufewa, ko kuma har zuwa karfe 10 na safe (0200GMT) a ranar Litinin 27 ga watan Yuli.
China ta tuhumi wasu ma'aikata a ofishin jakadancin Chengdu da cewa "suna gudanar da ayyukan da ba su dace da halayensu ba".
Ba tare da bayar da cikakken bayani ba, mai magana da yawun ma'aikatar harkokin wajen kasar Sin, Wang Wenbin ya ce irin wannan aiki ya tsoma baki cikin harkokin kasar Sin, ya kuma cutar da manufofinta na tsaron kasar.
An bayar da umarnin China na rufe ofishin jakadancin da ke Chengdu a ranar Juma'a don ramuwar gayya kan umarnin Amurka na rufe ofishin jakadancin China a Houston, Texas.
Washington ta umarci China da ta rufe ofishin Houston "don kare ikon mallakar ilmi na Amurka da kuma bayanan sirri na Amurkawa."
Yayin da rufe ofishin jakadancin kasar Sin a Houston ya fara aiki a ranar Juma'a, an ga wasu maza da suka bayyana a matsayin jami'an Amurka sun kutsa kai zuwa wurin ta wata kofa ta baya.
Wang ya ce a ranar Asabar cewa ya sabawa yarjejeniyar kasa da kasa da kuma bangarorin biyu kuma kasar Sin za ta mayar da martani, ba tare da tantance yadda za a yi ba.
Rufe dokar ta-baci ya kara haifar da tashin hankalin da ke tsakanin kasashen biyu kan batutuwa kama daga harkokin kasuwanci da leken asiri na masana'antu zuwa hakkokin bil'adama.
MDD ta ce dubban 'yan gwagwarmayar Pakistan a Afghanistan
ISLAMABAD - Wani rahoto na Amurka ya ce sama da 'yan tawayen Pakistan 6,000 ne ke boye a Afghanistan, mafi yawansu na cikin kungiyar 'yan Taliban da aka haramta a Pakistan da ke da alhakin kai hari kan sojoji da fararen hula na Pakistan.
Rahoton da aka fitar a wannan makon ya ce kungiyar, wacce aka fi sani da Tehreek-e-Taliban (TTP), ta danganta ta da kungiyar 'yan kishin Islama ta Afghanistan.
Wasu daga cikin 'ya'yan kungiyar TTP har sun shiga kungiyar IS wacce ke da hedkwatarta a gabashin Afghanistan.
Gwamnatin Afghanistan ba ta mayar da martani a ranar Lahadi ga buƙatun da Associated Press ta yi don yin sharhi ba.
Rahoton ya ce kungiyar IS a Afghanistan, wacce aka fi sani da IS a lardin Khorasan, ta sha da kyar a hannun jami'an tsaron Afghanistan da sojojin Amurka da na NATO, har ma a wasu lokutan kungiyar Taliban ta Afghanistan.
Kungiyar masu sa ido kan nazari da takunkumi ta Amurka ce ta shirya rahoton, wacce ke bin diddigin kungiyoyin ta'addanci a duniya.
Rahoton ya kiyasta cewa mambobin kungiyar IS a Afghanistan sun kai 2,200, kuma yayin da shugabancinta ya ragu, IS har yanzu tana cikin shugabanninta wani dan kasar Siriya Abu Said Muhammad al-Khorasani.
Rahoton ya kuma ce tawagar masu sa ido sun samu bayanin cewa wasu manyan kwamandojin gwamnatin Musulunci biyu, Abu Qutaibah da Abu Hajar al-Iraqi, sun isa Afghanistan ne kwanan nan daga Gabas ta Tsakiya.
"Duk da cewa a yankin ja da baya, (Islamic State) ya ci gaba da iya kai manyan hare-hare a sassa daban-daban na kasar, ciki har da Kabul.
Hakan na nufin jan hankalin mayakan Taliban da ke adawa da yarjejeniyar da Amurka," in ji rahoton, yana mai nuni da yarjejeniyar zaman lafiya da Amurka ta kulla da Taliban a watan Fabrairu.
An cimma wannan yarjejeniyar ne domin baiwa Amurka damar kawo karshen ayyukanta na shekaru 19 a Afghanistan, kuma ta yi kira ga 'yan Taliban da su ba da tabbacin cewa kungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda ba za su yi amfani da yankinsu ba.
Har ila yau, ana sa ran yarjejeniyar za ta ba da tabbacin sa hannun kungiyar Taliban a yaki da kungiyar IS.
Bangare na biyu kuma mai yiwuwa mafi muhimmanci na yarjejeniyar ya bukaci tattaunawa tsakanin Taliban da shugabancin siyasa na Kabul.
A ranar Asabar da ta gabata, ma'aikatar harkokin wajen Amurka ta fitar da wata sanarwa da ke cewa, wakilin zaman lafiyarta Zalmay Khalilzad ya sake jigila ta yankin yana mai neman tsallakewa a fara tattaunawar, wacce aka dakatar da ita sau da yawa yayin da bangarorin biyu ke jayayya kan shirin sakin fursunoni.
Yarjejeniyar da ke goyon bayan Amurka ta yi kira ga gwamnatin Afghanistan da ta saki fursunonin Taliban 5,000 da kuma 'yan Taliban don 'yantar da ma'aikatan gwamnati da sojoji 1,000 a matsayin abin da ake kira kyakkyawan nufi gabanin tattaunawa.
Har zuwa yanzu gwamnati ta ki sakin fursunoni kusan 600 'yan Taliban da ta kira manyan masu laifi kuma ta yi tayin ba da wasu hanyoyi.
'Yan Taliban sun ki amincewa.
Sanarwar Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Amurka ta ce "jam'iyyun sun fi kusa da fara tattaunawar cikin gida da Afghan, muhimmin mataki na gaba na kawo karshen yakin Afghanistan na tsawon shekaru 40."
"Duk da cewa an samu gagarumin ci gaba kan musayar fursunoni, amma lamarin na bukatar karin kokari domin magancewa sosai."
Mai magana da yawun harkokin siyasa na kungiyar Taliban a farkon makon nan ta ce a shirye ta ke ta gudanar da tattaunawa da shugabannin siyasa na Kabul bayan hutun addinin Musulunci na Eid al-Adha a karshen watan da ya gabata, lamarin da ya sa aka kammala sakin fursunonin.
Babban abin damuwa ga Pakistan shi ne kasancewar 'yan gwagwarmaya a Afghanistan, musamman wadanda ke da nasaba da TTP ko Jamaat-ul-Ahrar ko Lashkar-e-Islam, da kuma wadanda ke tare da sojojin 'yanci na Baluchistan, wadanda suka dauki alhakin kai manyan hare-hare a wannan watan a kudancin lardin Sindh da kuma kudu maso yammacin lardin Baluchistan.
An kashe sojojin Pakistan da dama a wannan watan a kudu maso yammacin lardin Baluchistan a yaki da 'yan tawayen.
Kungiyar TTP ta dauki alhakin kai daya daga cikin mummunan harin da aka kai a Pakistan a shekarar 2014, lokacin da aka kaiwa wata makarantar sojojin Pakistan hari sannan aka kashe mutane 140.
Yawancin dalibai ne, wasu kuma matasa ne 5.
"An kiyasta adadin mayakan ta'addanci na kasashen waje na Pakistan a Afghanistan, wanda ke zama barazana ga kasashen biyu, a tsakanin 6,000 zuwa 6,500, yawancinsu suna da TTP," in ji rahoton.
Babban bankin Birtaniya HSBC ya musanta "kafa tarko" ga kamfanin Huawei na kasar Sin a binciken Amurka - RT Labaran Kasuwanci
Babban bankin kasa da kasa mai hedkwata a birnin London HSBC ya kai dauki ga kafofin watsa labarun cewa ba haka ba ne, kamar yadda kafofin watsa labaran kasar Sin suka yi ikirarin cewa, "kera hujjoji" a kan Huawei, wanda ya kai ga kama babban jami'in kudi na kamfanin a Kanada.
A wani sako da ya wallafa a shafinsa na WeChat, mai ba da lamuni ya ce ayyukanta ba su haifar da binciken da Amurka ta yi kan babbar mai sayar da kayayyakin sadarwa na sadarwa a duniya ba, yayin da binciken da kamfanin Huawei ya yi kan zargin keta takunkumin Amurka kan Iran ya fara ne tun kafin hannun bankin a karshen shekarar 2016.
"HSBC ba ta da wata kiyayya ga Huawei kuma ba ta "tsarin" Huawei ba," in ji bankin a ranar Asabar, inda ya kara da cewa ba za ta taba gurbata wasu hujjoji game da abokan kasuwancinta ba.
"Da yake mayar da martani ga buƙatun US DOJ [Sashen Shari'a na Amurka] na neman bayanai, kungiyar HSBC ta gabatar da hujjoji na haƙiƙa.
HSBC bai "ƙirƙira" shaida ko " ɓoye" hujjoji ba."
Har ila yau a rt.com matakin da Birtaniya ta dauka na hana Huawei daga cibiyar sadarwa ta 5G ya nuna cewa Amurka ta umurci manufofin harkokin waje na Birtaniya - George Galloway ga Boom Bust
An toshe sakon a dandalin tare da rubuta cewa "ya sabawa ka'idoji" kuma ba a samu ba a yanzu.
Sanarwar na zuwa ne jim kadan bayan da wasu kafofin yada labarai na kasar Sin, ciki har da jaridun da ke da alaka da jihar, suka zargi HSBC da "cigaba" da Washington don kafa wa kamfanin Huawei tarko.
Kamfanin ya kasance a cibiyar wani abin kunya na diplomasiyya fiye da shekara daya da rabi tun lokacin da aka kama shugaban kamfanin Huawei Meng Wanzhou a watan Disamba na shekarar 2018 a Kanada bisa takardar izini daga Amurka.
Meng na fuskantar tuhume-tuhume na zamba saboda zargin yin amfani da kamfanin harsashi wajen kakaba wa Iran takunkumi da kuma zargin yi wa bankuna karya game da alakar da ke tsakanin Huawei da kamfanin Skycom na Iran.
A cewar sabbin shaidun da jaridar Global Times ta ambata, HSBC ta san dangantakar kamfanin kasar Sin da Skycom.
An bayar da rahoton cewa bankin ya yanke shawarar "kauracewa" da gwamnatin Amurka don tserewa daga hukunci mai tsanani a shekarar 2012, lokacin da bankin ya yarda da haramcin kudi da kuma keta takunkumi, ciki har da takunkumi kan Iran.
An umarce shi a lokacin da ya biya bashin kudi kimanin dala biliyan 1.9 da kuma hana duk wani laifi makamancin haka.
"Hujjojin sun nuna cewa HSBC ta fahimci wannan dangantaka amma da gangan ta sayar da takardun kasuwancin kwastominta na sirri ga bangaren Amurka don gwamnatin Amurka ta yi watsi da kuskuren da bankin Birtaniya ya yi, kuma ba za ta hukunta shi ba a karkashin yarjejeniyar tsare-tsare ta 2012", jaridar ta ce a daya daga cikin labarinta game da batun.
A cikin gargadin da ta yi a rufe, jaridar da ke kula da birnin Beijing ta kara da cewa, mai ba da rancen, idan aka tabbatar da cewa yana da laifin wannan "hadari", zai iya fuskantar "horo mai tsanani" a kasar Sin, daya daga cikin manyan kasuwanni na HSBC.
Wannan dai ba shi ne karon farko da mashahurin bankin ke fuskantar wuta ba a'yan makonnin nan.
A watan da ya gabata, HSBC ta sha alwashin goyon bayan sabuwar dokar tsaron kasa ga Hong Kong, birnin da kasuwancinta ya fara kuma wanda ya kai fiye da rabin ribarsa.
Bankin ya fuskanci zarge-zarge daga bangarorin biyu - daga kasashen Yamma, inda Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya kira wannan tallafi a matsayin "kamfanoni kowanne hali" da kuma Gabas, inda bangaren China ya bayar da rahoton cewa, goyon bayan da yake bayarwa "ya yi watsi da shi".
Masu kashe gobara sun sami ƙasa a gundumar Lassen
Masu kashe gobara na samun karbuwa a kan gobarar daji biyu da ta kone fiye da kadada 30,000 a gundumar Lassen da ke arewa maso gabashin Sacramento.
Wutar Zinariya, wacce ta fara kudu da Adin, tana dauke da kashi 40% yayin da take ci gaba da barazana ga gidaje da gonaki da aikin noma da dabbobi da katako, in ji jami'an kashe gobara a wani sabuntawa a ranar Asabar da safe.
Bayan cin wuta na tsawon kwanaki hudu, gobarar ta tauna fadin eka 21,000, ta lalata gidaje bakwai sannan ta tura masu kashe gobara biyu zuwa asibiti.
A cikin dare, masu kashe gobara sun yi amfani da yanayi mai sauki don gina da kuma karfafa layin sarrafawa.
Amma ana sa ran iska mai guguwa da kuma karancin zafi har zuwa ranar Asabar.
Yammacin Susanville, wata karamar gobara da aka fi sani da Hog wuta ta lalata gine-gine biyu kuma ta cinye kimanin eka 10,000.
Wutar ta kwanta cikin dare yayin da masu kashe gobara suka yi aiki wajen sarrafawa tare da karfafa layukan sarrafawa, a cewar ma'aikatar kula da gandun daji da kare gobara ta California.
Ya zuwa safiyar Asabar, kashi 45% ne ke dauke da shi kuma sun yi kwanaki shida suna cin wuta.
A lokacin zafi na rana, da yanayin zafi sama da digiri 90 a yankin Susanville, wuraren shakatawa suna cikin haɗarin farfadowa.
Yayin da ake barin wasu mazauna gidajensu su koma gidajensu, wasu wuraren da ke wuraren kashe gobara biyu suna karkashin umarnin kwashewa.
An sako masu kashe gobara biyu da suka ji rauni a gobarar Gold daga asibiti.
Algeria: Mutuwar Mahmoud Guemama - Algeria Ta Yi Asarar Wani Dan Takarar Shugaban Kasa, In ji Shugaba Tebboune.
Shugaban kasar Algiers, Abdelmadjid Tebboune, ya aike da sakon ta'aziyya ga 'yan majalisar wakilan jama'ar kasar (APN), Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, wanda ya rasu a ranar Juma'a, inda ya ce kasar Algeria "ta rasa wani dan kishin kasa da kuma wani dan gwagwarmaya da ya aikata ga al'ummarsa da kuma al'ummarsa."
Algeria ta yi asara a yau, ta hanyar rasuwar Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama, dan kishin kasa kuma dan gwagwarmaya da ya jajirce kan al'ummarsa da kuma al'ummarsa, mutumin da bai taba yin kasa a gwiwa ba, wanda azama ta kasance cikakke tun daga lokacin da ya dauki makami, tare da jaruman 'yan'uwansa Mujahedeen, har zuwa numfashinsa na karshe a wannan rana ta bakin ciki da kawai za mu yi murabus da nufin Allah", Shugaba Tebboune ya rubuta a sakonsa na ta'aziyya.
"Marigayi Mahmoud Guemama, zaman lafiya ya tabbata a gare shi, ya kasance cikin ƙarni na musamman na 'yan kishin ƙasa masu aminci wadanda suka sadaukar da kansu don ƙasarsu", ya kara da cewa shugaban Jamhuriyar.
"Marigayin ya sadaukar da rayuwarsa ga 'yantar da Aljeriya daga azabtarwar mulkin mallaka, ta hanyar shiga cikin sahun juyin juya halin da aka yi a farkon rayuwa a shekarar 1960 a sansanin horarwa na Tahart na tarihi mai lamba VI."
Shugaba Tebboune ya ce "marigayi shugaban kasa sananne ne ga kowa saboda irin karfin da ya ke da shi da kuma irin jajircewar da ya ke yi na ganin an kafa kasar Algeria mai arziki da hadin kai.
"A kudanci mai nisa, marigayi Mahmud Guemama ya yi suna sosai a matsayin mai shiga tsakani, yana mai shiga tsakani domin sulhunta 'yan'uwa a kasa guda a duk lokacin da aka hura wutar sabani" Shugaban ya kara da cewa a sakonsa.
"Dukkanin wadannan halaye da dabi'u sun sa marigayi Mahmoud Guemama girmamawa da amincewar mutanen Tamanrasset wadanda suka zabe shi ya wakilce su a majalisar wakilan jama'a ta kasa (APN) saboda sharudda da dama, a yayin da ya kasance jakada kuma mai kare damuwar yankin da burin al'ummarta, har ma da wakili da kakakin dukkanin 'yan Algeria", in ji shugaban kasar.
"Dukkanin maganganu na ta'aziyya ba za su isa su jinjina wa Mahmud Guemama ba, aminci ya tabbata a gare shi.
Yana barinmu a yau a daidai lokacin da kasar Aljeriya ta bukace shi," a cewar shugaban kasar.
"Ina rokon Allah madaukakin sarki da ya kewaye marigayin da rahamarsa mai tsarki, ya marabce shi a aljannarsa mai dimbin yawa tare da shuhadaa da nagarta.
Ina kuma addu'ar Allah ya baiwa iyalansa da masoyansa hakuri da ta'aziyya...babu wani karfi ko karfi sai da Allah" Shugaban kasar ya kammala.
Zanga-zangar Seattle: An yi ruwan wuta da barkono a yayin da dubban mutane ke tafiya a birni
SEATTLE - Bayan makonni na tashe-tashen hankula tsakanin masu zanga-zanga da hukumomin tarayya a Portland, Ore, taron mutane kimanin 2,000 sun yi tattaki a Seattle a ranar Asabar, suna tafiya a kan tituna tare da yin arangama da 'yan sanda.
Jami'an 'yan sanda uku sun ji rauni, ciki har da wanda aka kwantar da shi a asibiti da wani rauni a kafa sakamakon wani abin fashewa, kuma an kama masu zanga-zanga 16 tun da yamma, in ji 'yan sanda.
Dauke da alamomi kamar su "Feds Go Home" da kuma rera taken "Babu adalci, babu zaman lafiya", masu zanga-zangar sun tsaya a wurin da ake tsare da matasa a nan gaba tare da cinnawa gine-gine wuta a wurin.
Wasu sun fasa tagogin kasuwancin da ke kusa.
'Yan sanda sun fuskanci cunkoson jama'a a unguwar Capitol Hill, inda suka tura gurbataccen ruwa da kuma feshin barkono kafin su fara daukar mutane a tsare.
Bipasha Mukherjee, 'yar shekara 52, na Kirkland, Wash, ta ce tana zanga-zanga a kan tituna tun watan Mayu kuma ta ce abin damuwa ne a gare ta ganin irin wadannan dabaru na 'yan sanda.
"Wannan ba ita ce kasar da na yi hijira ba," a cewar Misis Mukherjee, wacce ta zo daga Indiya sama da shekaru 30 da suka gabata.
"Yana jin kamar muna hanzarin zama jihar fasaha da kuma 'yan sanda."
Michaud Savage na Seattle ya ce zanga-zangar na nufin duka kananan hukumomi ne da kuma tura jami'an gwamnatin tarayya wadanda suka janyo cece-kuce kan zanga-zangar da aka dade ana yi a Portland.
Mista Savage ya ce dabarun tilasta bin doka a Portland, wadanda suka hada da amfani da iskar gas da kuma garkuwa da jama'a, suna da hatsari kuma ba su dace ba.
Mista Savage ya ce a yayin da yake wanke idanunsa da feshin barkono kuma ya ji masa rauni a hannunsa daga gurbataccen ruwa.
Mutuwar George Floyd a hannun 'yan sanda a Minneapolis a watan Mayu ya yi watsi da zanga-zangar jama'a da ta jawo miliyoyin mutane a kan tituna a birane da dama, amma zanga-zangar ta ragu a yawancin birane.
Seattle da Portland, duk da haka, sun ga tsawaita zanga-zanga.
Masu zanga-zangar a Seattle a wani lokaci sun yi ikirarin wasu tubalan unguwar Capitol Hill kuma sun ayyana wani yanki mai cin gashin kai.
Bayan jerin harbe-harbe da aka yi a wurin ya sa 'yan sanda suka share yankin, zanga-zangar ta ragu.
Portland, a halin yanzu, ya ci gaba da zanga-zanga, tare da wasu daga cikin zanga-zanga mafi tsanani a kusa da gine-ginen tarayya a birnin.
Bayan da shugaba Trump ya bayar da umarnin zartarwa don kare mutum-mutumi da dukiyar gwamnatin tarayya, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta cikin gida ta tura tawagogin dabara zuwa birnin, inda ta fara jerin rikice-rikice da suka yi sanadiyyar raunata masu zanga-zangar, binciken babban jami'in bincike da kuma kira daga shugabannin yankin don jami'an tarayya su tafi.
Taron masu zanga-zanga a wannan birnin ya karu zuwa dubban mutane, kuma ana ci gaba da zanga-zanga a wajen.
A wannan makon, jami'an tarayya sun tura wata tawagar dabara zuwa Seattle, kuma masu zanga-zangar sun ambaci wannan ci gaban a matsayin dalili daya na zanga-zangar ranar Asabar.
Yayin da zanga-zangar Portland ta tsakiya a cikin gari, zanga-zangar a ranar Asabar ta yi tafiya a yankunan da ke gabashin tsakiyar gari, inda gidan kotun tarayya na birnin yake.
Virginia Beach ta saukar da abin tunawa da kungiyar kwadago
VIRGINIA BEACH, Va. - Birnin Virginia Beach ya cire wani abin tunawa da 'yan kungiyar Confederate mai shekaru 115 daga filayen jama'a a ranar Asabar, kasa da kwanaki biyu bayan da Majalisar City ta zabe shi baki daya.
Ma'aikata sun saukar da ginin mai tsawon kafa 27 (mita 8.2) a safiyar ranar Asabar, kamar yadda kafafen yada labarai suka ruwaito.
An naɗa shi a shekara ta 1905 kuma ya tsaya a wajen tsohuwar gidan kotun Yarima Anne County, a daidai wurin da aka taɓa yin gwanjon bayi.
'Yan majalisa sun kada kuri'a baki daya ranar Alhamis da daddare domin fara aikin cire shi.
Majalisar ta saurari jawabai da dama kuma ta yanke shawarar cewa mutane da yawa suna kallon wannan ginin a matsayin rarrabuwa da kuma tunatarwa mai zafi game da abubuwan da suka gabata.
A kwanan nan an rufe mutum-mutumi gaba daya, tare da kulle kofa a kusa da shi bayan zanga-zangar da aka yi a baya-bayan nan da kuma zanga-zangar da aka yi a wasu gidajen tarihi na Confederate.
Za a ajiye abin tunawa a yanzu.
Yanzu dole ne birnin ya jira duk wani tayi daga kungiyoyin tarihi ko wasu abokai da za su so su dauki abin tunawa.
Kotun Masar ta ce mutumin da ya kashe yara uku ya yi nazarin tabin hankali
Babban Mai Shari'a na Kudancin Minya Tamer Motea a ranar Lahadi ya yanke wa wani manomi hukuncin zaman gidan yari na kwanaki hudu a lokacin da ake bincike kan dalilin da ya sa ya kashe 'ya'yansa uku yayin da kuma ya kai shi ga kwamitin kula da masu tabin hankali.
A ranar 24 ga watan Yuli, Mohamed Ali dan shekara 56 ya jefar da 'ya'yansa Khadiga, hudu, Mena takwas, da kuma Omar, shida, a gaban jirgin kasa mai tafiya a tashar jirgin kasa ta Mallawi.
An gano cewa Ali yana babbakewa ba tare da hadin kai ba a lokacin da ake gudanar da bincike, wanda hakan ya haifar da tuhumar cewa yana fama da tashe-tashen hankali.
Matarsa ta musanta cewa ta yi fama da wata matsala da shi kuma ta danganta halayyarsa da tabin hankali.
Mazauna kauyen Massart Mallawi sun daina magana kan lamarin, inda suka yi ta'aziyya kawai ga iyalan yaran.
Kusan kashi 93 cikin 100 na yaran Masar 'yan shekara daya zuwa 14 na fama da tashin hankali, in ji Khalid Darwish, mai ba da shawara ga majalisar kula da yara da 'yan uwa ta kasar a watan Oktoba.
Shari'a na daya daga cikin muhimman ginshikan kawar da cin zarafin yara, ya kara da cewa, yana mai jaddada muhimmancin hadin gwiwa tsakanin majalisa da hukunta jama'a a wannan bangare.
A cewar wani bincike da Hukumar Kula da Yara da Uwa ta Kasa ta shirya, ana fuskantar tashin hankali a wuraren da ya kamata a zauna lafiya, kamar gida, makaranta ko kulake, da kuma fuskantar tashin hankali daga mutanen da ya kamata su kula da su, kamar iyaye ko malamai.
'Yan kwadago masu tsattsauran ra'ayi sun bukaci a kori Corbyn ko kuma su fuskanci kara
Labour zai iya biya diyya na tsakanin £ 3million zuwa £ 8million, a cewar rahotanni.
Yanzu haka shugaba Keir Starmer na fuskantar matsin lamba na korar Mista Corbyn.
A daren jiya tsohon ma'aikatan jam'iyyar sun ce za su sauke matakin shari'a idan aka kori Mista Corbyn daga jam'iyyar.
Ya zuwa yanzu dai jam'iyyar Labour ta ki yin tsokaci kan bukatar.
Sai dai dan majalisar kwadago Jon Trickett ya ce: " Bukata ce ta ban dariya."
Masu goyon bayan Mista Corbyn sun ce Mista Starmer ya bukaci mayar da hankali kan magance matsalar Tories kan cutar Koronabirus maimakon komawa cikin kungiyoyin kwadago na cikin gida.
Wata majiya daga jam'iyyar Labour ta fadawa jaridar Daily Mail cewa za su dauki matakin shari'a ko da Mista Starmer ya kori Mista Corbyn.
"Ina nufin da gaske ne, ya sa jam'iyyar Labour ta sake yin takara."
"Har yanzu akwai wata hanya mai nisa da ya kamata a ci gaba da siyasa amma ya fara da ban sha'awa sosai kuma ya shiga wani yanayi inda ga mutane da yawa da suka bar jam'iyyar Labour da gaske, masu jefa kuri'a kamar yadda suke, ina ganin yanzu suna sake kallon hakan sosai kuma suna ɗaukarsa a matsayin wani mutum mai tsanani."
Mista Blair ya damu da cewa har yanzu ana ganin Labour a matsayin jam'iyyar da ke kara haraji.
Ya ce: "Abubuwan da na fuskanta game da haraji a lokacin da kake cikin jam'iyyar Labour suna mai da hankali sosai saboda jama'a da ke waje ba sa zaune a wurin suna damuwa ko za ku kara haraji ko a'a, mai yiwuwa suna damuwa cewa za ku kara haraji don haka kawai ku tuna da wannan damuwa."
Covid-19 za ta sauya tattalin arzikin duniya har abada (ra'ayi)
Binciken kwayar cutar zai iya zama wani bangare na rayuwarmu, kamar dai yadda matakan tsaro suka zama ruwan dare bayan 9/11.
Yana da muhimmanci a zuba jari a cikin kayayyakin da ake bukata don gano barkewar kwayar cutar a nan gaba.
Wannan zuba jari na kare tattalin arziki idan rigakafi ga Covid-19 ya zama na ɗan lokaci.
Yawancin tattalin arziki sun karbi nau'in tallafin Kurzarbeit na Jamus a lokacin annobar.
Wannan siyasa ta rike ma'aikata aiki a rage sa'o'i da biyan albashi, tare da gwamnati ta biya wasu daga cikin karancin albashi.
Ta hanyar ajiye wasanni tsakanin kamfanoni da ma'aikata, tattalin arziki ya fi dacewa a shirye don farfadowa cikin sauri.
Yana da muhimmanci a inganta aiwatar da wadannan manufofi da kuma sanya su zama wani bangare na dindindin na kayan aikinmu na farfado da tattalin arziki.
Aiki mai nisa zai zama ruwan dare gama gari.
Muna da wasu hujjoji da ke nuna cewa aiki daga gida yana da amfani sosai kamar aiki a ofishin.
Duk da haka, kamfanoni da yawa sun yi jinkirin rungumar aiki na nesa.
Yanzu da mutane da yawa sun gwada shi da kyakkyawan sakamako, aikin nesa na iya kasancewa a nan don zama.
Matsalar annobar ta hanzarta saurin sauya fasalin zamani, tare da kara fadada kasuwancin e-commerce da kuma karuwar saurin karɓar telemedicine, videoconferencing, koyarwa ta yanar gizo da kuma fintech.
Kamfanoni masu samar da kayayyaki na kasa da kasa suna fuskantar karanci da kuma cutar kwalara.
Mai yiwuwa za mu ga yawancin wadannan kamfanoni sun sake samar da wasu kayayyakin da suke samarwa.
Abin takaici, wannan yanayin ba zai haifar da ayyukan yi da yawa ba saboda yawancin abubuwan da ake samarwa suna iya sarrafa kansu.
Gwamnatoci za su fi girma bayan sun taka rawar inshorar da kuma saka hannun jari na karshe a lokacin rikicin.
bashin da jama'a za su ci, zai haifar da kalubalen kudi a duniya.
Darasi mafi muhimmanci daga annobar Covid-19 shi ne muhimmancin yin aiki tare kan matsalolin da suka shafi dan adam baki daya.
Mu ne mafi karfi da haɗin kai fiye da rarrabuwa.
Sarauniya da Adam Lambert: Brian May na murnar zagayowar ranar haihuwar Roger Taylor
Jaridar Sarauniya ta ba da labarin ranar haihuwarsa a yau tare da mai gabatar da kara na Rolling Stones Mick Jagger, wanda yanzu yake da shekaru 77 da haihuwa.
Brian May ya yi bikin zagayowar ranar haihuwarsa karo na 73 a karshen mako a ranar 19 ga watan Yuli kuma ya yi godiya ga magoya bayan da suka yi murnar zagayowar ranar haihuwar.
Tauraron dan wasan ya rubuta a wani rubutu da ya yi kusa da shi da matarsa Anita Dobson cewa: "Abincin dare na ranar haihuwa a gare ni - wanda Anita ta kirkiro - mun yi ado don mu zauna a gida!"
Sakataren Cikin Gida Priti Patel ya bukaci bayani daga Twitter da Instagram a kan 'abun ciki' Wiley tweets
Priti Patel ta bukaci bayani daga Twitter da Instagram a tsawon lokacin da aka dauka don cire sakonnin da Wiley ya yi.
A halin yanzu 'yan sanda suna bincike kan wasu kalamai na jayayya da aka wallafa a asusun mai zane-zane na Grime a kafofin watsa labarun.
Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida ya bayyana a ranar Lahadi cewa: "Sakamakon jayayya daga Wiley abin kunya ne."
"Bai kamata ba su samu damar ci gaba da kasancewa a Twitter da Instagram na tsawon lokaci ba kuma na nemi cikakken bayani a kansu."
"Dole ne kamfanonin kafofin watsa labarun su yi aiki da sauri don kawar da irin wannan kiyayya mai ban tsoro daga dandalin su."
An zargi Twitter da "karin jayayya" yayin da har yanzu ana ganin tweets na Wiley sa'o'i 12 bayan da aka fara sanya su.
Tun daga lokacin an cire wasu tweets kuma an sanyawa dan shekara 41-shekara dokar hana fita na tsawon kwanaki bakwai ta shafin.
A baya Twitter ya ce an kulle asusun Wiley na wani dan lokaci "saboda keta manufofinmu na nuna kyama", yayin da Facebook ya ce "babu wani wuri na kalaman nuna kyama a shafin Instagram."
'Yan sandan birni sun ce a ranar Asabar: "Ganawar tana daukar dukkan rahotannin jayayya da matukar muhimmanci, ana tantance abubuwan da suka dace."
A halin yanzu, kamfanin gudanarwa na Wiley, A-List Management, "ya yanke dukkanin dangantaka" da tauraron.
Tsohon manajan mai zane-zane a yanzu, John Woolf, wanda Yahudawa ne, ya rubuta a dandalin sada zumunta na Twitter cewa: "Bayan tweets na jayayya na Wiley a yau mu a @A_ListMGMT mun yanke dukkanin alaka da shi. Babu wani wuri a cikin al'umma don jayayya."
A baya ya ce bai goyi bayan ko kuma ya amince da abin da Wiley ya wallafa ba, amma zai yi magana da shi a asirce kuma "ta taimaka wajen ilmantar da shi."
Sai dai a wani bidiyo a shafin sada zumunta na Instagram, Wiley ya bayyana cewa shi ne ya yanke alaka da gudanarwarsa.
Sauran 'yan majalisar sun zargi Twitter saboda barin tweets su kasance a bayyane.
Kwamitin kwadago Jess Phillips ya ce a ranar Asabar:
"Kawai ga dukkanin kayan Wiley. Me ya sa a duniya @Twitter ta bar irin wannan tsattsauran ra'ayi na jayayya da ƙiyayya? Tana fuskantar dukkanin mummunan bugun jini, Yahudawa suna samun abubuwan da ba ku samu ba, suna da iko, suna tunanin cewa sun fi kyau... Wannan abu ne mai haɗari. Tabbas ya kamata ya sauka."
Dan majalisa Neil Coyle ya kara da cewa: "Gudanarwarsa na iya yin aiki da sauri fiye da @Twitter yana mai jaddada cewa, dokar (ciki har da Lissafin Harms na Yanar Gizo) ya kamata ta tabbatar da cewa ba a amfani da dandamali na kafofin watsa labarun don yada kiyayya ba."
John Mann, mashawarci mai zaman kansa na gwamnati a kan jayayya, ya ce tweets "ya nuna ainihin dalilin da ya sa doka ke bukatar canzawa don rike su zuwa lissafi mai kyau."
A halin yanzu, Gangamin Yaki da Cin Hanci ya bukaci 'yan sanda da su bincika abubuwan da Wiley ya yi, kuma ya yi kira ga a rufe asusunsa na kafofin watsa labarun "don hana ci gaba da zubar da dafin Yahudawa."
Wiley, wanda aka fi sani da Godfather of Grime wanda ainihin sunansa Richard Cowie, ya karbi MBE don ayyukan waƙa a 2018.
"kashe-kashe" da Amurka ke yi na dakile neman magungunan cutar Koronabirus
Ƙoƙarin da duniya ke yi na samar da magungunan yaki da cutar Covid mai amfani na kawo cikas ga Amurka saboda masu bincike suna gwajin magunguna ta "hanyar da ba ta dace ba", ƙwararren masanin da ke jagorantar shirin na Burtaniya ya yi gargadin.
Shirin farfado da cutar Birtaniya, wanda ya shafi marasa lafiya 12,000 a asibitocin Birtaniya da yawa, ya riga ya gano wani sabon magani mai ban al'ajabi don magance cutar sannan kuma ya nuna wasu biyu - wanda a baya ake zaton cewa masu ceton rai ne - a matsayin marasa amfani.
Amma gazawar tsarin kiwon lafiya na Amurka ya dace da wannan fitarwa ya sa sauran magunguna masu ban al'ajabi da za a iya sharewa don amfani da su sosai, har yanzu ba a tantance su ba.
Musamman ma, plasma mai dauke da kwayar cutar (blood plasma wanda aka dauka daga masu dauke da cutar Covid-19 wanda ke dauke da garkuwar jiki wanda zai iya kare wasu daga cutar) har yanzu ana gwada shi yadda ya kamata a wani babban gwaji na bazuwar cutar.
Farfesa Martin Landray, daya daga cikin wadanda suka kafa shirin farfado da cutar, ya ce "an riga an bai wa dubban mutane kwayar cutar plasma a Amurka amma ba a yi watsi da wadannan magunguna ba.
"Suna ba wa mutane kwayar cutar plasma ne kawai da fatan za ta yi aiki. An bayar da adadi mai yawa kuma har yanzu ba su san ko tana taimakawa ko cutarwa ko kuma ba ta da tasiri," in ji Landray, wani kwararre a fannin kafa manyan gwaje-gwajen magunguna.
Amurka ta kasa yin manyan gwaje-gwaje da bazuwar gwaji kuma hakan ya kawo karshen samar da magani mara kyau.
Gwajin magunguna marasa kyau sune ma'aunin zinare don gano magunguna masu amfani.
Suna cire nuna bambanci da ba a sani ba wanda zai iya haifar da hukuncin likitocin asibiti.
Ana bai wa dubban mutane magani sannan a ba dubban wasu magunguna.
Babu wanda ya san wanda aka ba su.
Sannan an kwatanta sakamako kuma an bayyana ingancin maganin.
Ta wannan hanyar, farfadowa ya iya nuna cewa steroid dexamethasone ya rage mutuwar da kashi uku a cikin marasa lafiyar Covid-19 a kan na'urar bada iska.
Haka kuma ya nuna cewa maganin hydroxychloroquine mai yawa - da kuma maganin hada-hadar magungunan lopinavir da ritonavir - ba su da wani tasiri wajen ceton rayukan marasa lafiya.
Abin da ya fi muhimmanci wadannan gwaje-gwaje suna bukatar adadin marasa lafiya da yawa kuma babu wani asibiti da ya isa ya yi irin wannan bincike.
Birtaniya ta sami wata fa'ida mai mahimmanci - Hukumar Kiwon Lafiya ta Kasa.
Sabanin haka, ma'aikatar kiwon lafiya ta Amurka ta rarrabu kuma nasararta kadai ta nuna yiwuwar magani ta nuna amfani da maganin remdesivir mai tsada sosai don hanzarta warkewar wasu marasa lafiya na Covid-19.
"Akwai gwajin kananan magunguna da yawa da suka shafi 'yan dozin ko 'yan daruruwan marasa lafiya da ke gudana a Amurka amma babu wani abu," in ji Landray.
"Sun kasa yin manyan gwaje-gwaje da bazuwar cutar kuma hakan ya kawo karshen samar da magani marar kyau. Hakan ya sa al'adar magani ba ta da kyau kuma sakamakon marasa lafiya ba shi da kyau."
Landray ya ce wannan gazawar ta yi matukar baƙin ciki idan aka yi la'akari da amfani da plasma mai dauke da cutar, wanda likitoci da yawa ke ganin zai iya taka muhimmiyar rawa wajen kula da marasa lafiya masu fama da cutar Covid-19.
"Idan ka kalli Amurka, an yi amfani da adadi mai yawa na wannan magani a kan wani abu mai ban sha'awa. Birtaniya ta fi dacewa idan aka kwatanta da abin da ke faruwa a can", ya kara da cewa.
Farfesa Peter Horby, wani kwararre a kan cututtuka da kuma wanda ya kafa shirin farfado da cututtuka, ya ce: "Akwai rahotannin marasa lafiya 20,000 da ke samun kwayar cutar plasma a wani lungu amma babu wani daga cikin wadanda suka kamu da cutar.
Da a ce sun saka wadannan marasa lafiya cikin gwaji na bazata, yanzu za mu samu cikakkiyar amsa game da ingancin kwayar cutar plasma."
Horby ya kara da cewa, a yanzu Burtaniya ta kaddamar da gwajin cutar plasma na bazata amma ba ta sa ran samun sakamako a shirye sai nan gaba a wannan shekarar.
Masar ta fara rijistar bayanan masu kada kuri'a a kasashen waje domin zaben 'yan majalisar dattijai
Hukumar Zabe ta Kasa (NEA) a ranar Asabar ta fara rijistar bayanan masu kada kuri'a a cikin jirgin domin fara jefa kuri'unsu a zaben'yan majalisar dattijai da za a gudanar a ranakun 9 da 10 ga watan Agusta, a cewar shafin intanet na NEA.
Dole ne masu jefa kuri'a su yi rajistar bayanan su da kuma aikin diplomasiyya da ke da alaƙa da mazauninsu a ƙasashen waje a shafin yanar gizo na NEA daga ranar 25 ga watan Yuli har zuwa ranar 31 ga watan Yuli.
Hukumar NEA ta kuma wallafa wani bidiyo da ke bayyana matakan da masu jefa kuri'a za su iya dauka don jefa kuri'arsu a nesa ta hanyar imel, a matsayin wani bangare na matakan kariya daga annobar coronavirus.
Lokacin shari'a na farfagandar zaben 'yan takarar majalisar dattijai ya gudana ne daga ranar 26 ga watan Yuli har zuwa ranar 8 ga watan Agusta, in ji NEA.
Ministan kula da harkokin shige da fice na Masar Nabila Makram ya yi kira ga 'yan kasar Masar masu kada kuri'a a kasashen waje da su shiga zaben a matsayin hakkinsu na tsarin mulki.
Majalisar wakilan Masar a ranar 17 ga watan Yuni ta amince da dokar kafa majalisar dattijai, wacce za ta yi aiki a matsayin babba a majalisar dokokin kasar.
An zartar da dokar ne da rinjaye kashi biyu cikin uku, tare da kin amincewa da wasu 'yan majalisar dokoki hudu
Majalisar za ta kunshi mambobi 300, 100 daga cikinsu an zabe su ne ta hanyar tsarin jerin sunayen da aka rufe, 100 an zabe su ne bisa tsarin daidaikun mutane, da kuma mambobi 100 da shugaban kasar ya nada
Wa'adin zama mamba a majalisar dattawa zai cika shekaru biyar, wanda zai fara daga ranar da za a fara ganawarsa ta farko.
Za a zabi sabuwar majalisar ne a cikin kwanaki sittin gabanin karshen wa'adin mulkinta.
'Yan sanda sun gwada sabbin kayan aiki marasa karfi yayin da zanga-zanga ke ci gaba
Yayin da ake ci gaba da fama da rikice-rikice tsakanin masu zanga-zanga da masu zanga-zanga a Portland da kewaye da kasar, ana ci gaba da muhawara kan yadda 'yan sanda za su iya yanke hukuncin kisa.
Wasu kamfanoni suna ci gaba da samar da sabbin kayan aiki na fasaha kamar na hannu mai nisa don 'yan sanda su yi amfani da su a maimakon zaɓuɓɓuka masu haɗari kamar fesa barkono, harsasai na roba da kuma gurbataccen walƙiya.
Kungiyar kare hakkin bil adama ta Amnesty International ta yi nazarin bidiyo 500 daga zanga-zangar daga ranar 26 ga watan Mayu zuwa ranar 5 ga watan Yuni kuma ta gano aukuwar karfi da ya wuce kima a jihohi 40 da kuma gundumar Columbia.
"Mun ga rashin amfani da iskar gas mai sa hawaye, da feshin barkono, da kwallayen barkono, da zagaye masu tasiri na tsawon millimita 40, ainihi duk wani nau'in makami marar karfi ana amfani da shi ta hanyoyin da ba su dace ba", a cewar Brian Castner, mai binciken makamai na kungiyar Amnesty International.
Duk da haka, wasu sun nace cewa samun zabin yana da muhimmanci don kaucewa bukatar bindiga.
Corey Pegues, tsohon mataimakin Sufeto na 'yan sanda na New York, ya ce "ya kamata dukkanin wadannan na'urori su kasance a hannun 'yan sanda su yi amfani da su ban da karfi na jiki da ake amfani da shi ta hanyar bindiga saboda ita kadai ce sana'a a Amurka inda 'yan ƙasa ke ba ku damar ɗaukar rayuwarku.
Daya daga cikin sababbin kayan aikin shine sunan Bola Wrap, na'urar hannu da ke harba igiyar Kevlar mai ƙafa 8 da ke kewaye da wanda ake zargi.
Akwai na'urorin Acoustic na dogon zango, wanda kuma aka fi sani da canons na sauti, da makaman makamashi da ke amfani da lasers don zafin fatar mutum, da sabbin kayan aikin da aka yi da su daga abubuwa kamar kumfa da zangarniya, da bama-bamai na stink, da kuma ba shakka Taser.
Hannun jari na Axon, kamfanin da ke yin Taser, ya kai sama da kashi 18%, wanda ya kai tsawon lokaci lokacin da zanga-zangar ta juya kwanaki bayan kisan George Floyd da 'yan sanda suka yi.
Ana sa ran kasuwar makamai marasa karfi za ta kai dala biliyan 11.85 nan da shekarar 2023.
Ku kalli bidiyon don duba sabbin kayan aiki na fasaha da 'yan sanda ke amfani da su don karfi mai karfi, yadda aka tsara su, da kuma abin da ke tattare da makomar 'yan sanda da kuma al'ummomin da suke hidima.
Magajin garin Kansas ya yi maraba da taimakon gwamnatin tarayya wajen magance kisan gilla, amma ya damu da muradin Trump
Magajin garin Kansas Quinton Lucas ya yi tambaya a ranar Lahadi kan dalilin Shugaba Trump na tura jami'an tsaro na tarayya zuwa biranen Amurka - yana mai cewa yayin da zai yi maraba da taimakon da aka bayar wajen magance kashe-kashen da aka yi a tsakiyar yammacin birnin, yana ganin matakin zai fi dacewa da samun damar sake zaben Trump.
"Na yi kyakkyawan takaici a wannan makon [cewa] shugaban kasar ya ambaci zanga-zangar George Floyd, ya ambaci yunkurin Black Lives Matter" Lucas, dan jam'iyyar Democrat, ya ce a "Fox News Lahadi" na zanga-zangar da aka yi a baya-bayan nan kan rashin daidaituwar launin fata da kuma zaluncin 'yan sanda.
"Ba haka lamarin yake ba a Kansas City. Mun samu karuwar shekara-shekara [amma] abin da muke bukatar taimako a kai shi ne a zahiri share wasu daga cikin kisan da ba a warware su ba."
Lucas ya kara da cewa: "Bari mu yi ƙoƙari mu mai da hankali kan magance kisan kai... Ina ganin idan kun saurari maganganun da aka yi a baya-bayan nan... muna farin cikin yin aiki tare da jami'an tsaro na tarayya cikin iyaka."
Duk da cewa a shirye yake ya sa jami'an tsaro na tarayya su yi aiki tare da masu bin doka a yankin, Lucas ya ce wannan rikici na Trump - musamman dangane da rigingimun da ke tattare da dabarun da jami'an gwamnatin tarayya ke amfani da su a Portland, Ore, ya sa yawancin 'yan majalisarsa su nuna damuwa game da kasancewar jami'an tsaro a titunan birnin.
"Abin da ba mu bukata ba shi ne karin wuta daga jami'an tsaro na tarayya da za su yi, ina tsammanin, wani lamari ne mai ban sha'awa na siyasa", in ji shi.
Trump a ranar Laraba ya sanar da cewa yana tura jami'an gwamnatin tarayya 100 zuwa Chicago don taimakawa wajen yaki da hauhawar wasu laifuka - wani yunkuri da ke nuna fadada sa hannun Fadar White House a kan tilasta bin doka a yankin yayin da Trump ke ci gaba da sanya kansa a matsayin shugaban "doka da oda".
"karuwar" jami'an da aka sanar a ranar Laraba zuwa Chicago da sauran biranen Amurka wani bangare ne na Operation Legend - wanda aka yi wa lakabi da LeGend Taliferro dan shekara 4 da haihuwa, wanda aka harbe shi a lokacin da yake barci a wani gida na Kansas City a karshen watan da ya gabata.
Yayin da tura jami'an gwamnatin tarayya don taimakawa masu bin doka a yankin ba wani abu ba ne - Babban Mai Shari'a Bill Barr ya sanar da irin wannan karuwar a watan Disamba ga birane bakwai da suka ga tashin hankali - irin wakilin tarayya da aka aika, da kuma wasu dabarunsu, sun tayar da damuwa tsakanin 'yan majalisar jihohi da na yankin.
'Yan majalisar dokoki da dama daga New York zuwa Portland sun yi kakkausar suka kan gwamnatin Trump na tura jami'an tsaro zuwa garuruwansu, musamman bayan rahotannin da ke cewa wasu jami'an gwamnatin tarayya da ba a san ko su wanene ba sun tsare masu zanga-zanga a Portland kuma sun tafi da su a cikin motocin da ba a nuna ba.
Portland ta fuskanci zanga-zanga a kusa da kullum a kan zaluncin 'yan sanda da kuma wariyar launin fata tun bayan mutuwar George Floyd yayin da yake tsare a hannun 'yan sanda a Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga watan Mayu.
Har ila yau, hukumomin karkara sun yi korafin cewa karuwar ta haifar da tashin hankali ne kawai, kuma masana shari'a masu laifi sun ce kokarin ya kauce wa bayanin saboda lokacin da Amurka ke rayuwa - tare da annoba, rashin aikin yi na tarihi da kuma yin la'akari da wariyar launin fata da kuma yadda 'yan sanda ke kula da mutanen launin fata.
AP ta dakatar da sakataren yada labarai na Fadar White House Kayleigh McEnany saboda tattaunawar "siyasa" - amma manema labarai suna ci gaba da yin tambayoyin siyasa - RT USA News
Jaridar Associated Press ta zargi sakatariyar yada labaran fadar White House Kayleigh McEnany da damuwa da kafofin yada labarai ta hanyar yi mata bayani ta fuskar siyasa maimakon bayanai - a bayyane ta manta cewa manema labarai sun zabi tambayoyin.
Wani labarin a ranar Asabar na kamfanin dillancin labarai na AP, mafi girma a Amurka, ya ce tattaunawar manema labarai na Fadar White House na iya zama "al'ada mai karyewa", kamar yadda McEnany ya sanya su "tallace-tallace mai zurfi ga shugaban kasa da ke fuskantar sake zabe, wurin kai hare-hare a kan kafofin watsa labarai da kuma dandalin tattaunawa kan bayanai" game da abin da gwamnati ke yi.
Na karshe daga cikin wadannan maganganu ba za a iya tabbatar da su ba, kamar yadda babu wani sabon bayani da aka bayyana a tattaunawar.
Abin da AP ta kasa ambata shi ne cewa babu wani sabon bayani da ake nema a zahiri a tattaunawar.
'Yan jarida na yawan amfani da 'yan jarida na fadar White House don jawo hankalin kansu, wani nau'i na fasaha da Jim Acosta na CNN ya kammala.
Suna wuce dangantakar kafofin watsa labarai masu adawa da juna, suna maimaita juna wajen yin tambayoyin gotcha da nufin tursasawa Shugaba Donald Trump kawai.
A wasu lokuta, suna mai da kansu labarai, kamar lokacin da jaridar CBS News Weijia Jiang ta mayar da martani ga wani "tambaya China" da Trump ya yi ta hanyar yin wani abin da bai dace ba game da wariyar launin fata: "Sir, me ya sa kake fadin hakan a gare ni musamman?"
Tattaunawar ranar 6 ga watan Yuli ta ba da misali mai kyau game da yadda tattaunawar ta daina zama tushen bayanai masu ma'ana ga Amurkawa.
A wani sako da ya wallafa a shafinsa na sada zumunta na Tuwita a safiyar yau, Trump ya bayyana cewa tashar talabijin ta NASCAR ta cutar da wani zargi na nuna kyama ga direba Bubba Wallace da kuma hukuncin da ta yanke na hana nuna tutar kungiyar kwadago a abubuwan da suka faru.
A tsinkaya, yawancin tambayoyin sun kasance game da tweet a matsayin mai rahoto bayan da mai rahoto ya tambayi McEnany tambayoyi da aka tsara don ya sa ta ce Trump na goyon bayan tutar Confederate.
McEnany ba ta bayar da amsar da manema labarai ke so ba - cizo mai sauti da zai cutar da Trump - amma ta mayar da martani sau da yawa ta hanyar cewa shugaban kasa ba ya daukar wani matsayi a tutar Confederate kuma abin da ya faru a sakonsa shi ne cewa an yi kuskuren nuna magoya bayan NASCAR a matsayin masu nuna wariyar launin fata.
AP ta ce ta yi "baƙin ciki" a lokacin tattaunawar.
Labarin na AP ya maimaita wani shafi na jaridar Washington Post a farkon watan nan na dan jaridar ABC News Jonathan Karl, wanda kuma shi ne shugaban kungiyar masu ba da amsa a fadar White House.
Karl ya yi jayayya da cewa, "karin gaskiya da kuma amfani da fadar White House a kan manufofi na siyasa kawai, keta yarda da jama'a ne."
Duk da haka hanzarin da McEnany ta yi da kuma salon kame-kame ya sa ta zama jarumar wasu magoya bayan Trump, tun bayan da ta gabatar da jawabinta na farko a ranar 1 ga watan Mayu bayan da ta karbi mukamin sakatariyar yada labarai a watan Afrilu.
'Yan jaridar sun shafe fiye da shekara guda kafin nadin nata.
Kamar sauran fannoni na rayuwar siyasa a Washington, dangantakar sakataren yada labarai na fadar White House da kafofin yada labarai ta sauya sosai a zamanin Trump.
Wannan canji ya fito ne daga bangarorin biyu kuma ya yi hasashen zuwan McEnany.
Tsohuwar sakatariyar yada labarai Sarah Huckabee Sanders ta hannun 'yar wasan kwaikwayo Michelle Wolf a wurin cin abincin dare na 'yan jarida na Fadar White House a watan Afrilun shekarar 2018 ta yi muni sosai har ma mai masaukin baki na MSNBC Mika Brzezinski ya kira shi "m."
Jill Colvin, 'yar jarida a fadar White House, ta gaishe da McEnany a jawabinta na farko ta hanyar tambayar cewa, "Shin za ku yi alkawarin cewa ba za ku taba yi mana karya ba daga wannan matsayi?"
Mai sharhi kan harkokin siyasa na Fox News Brit Hume, wani tsohon dan jarida da ya shafe sama da shekaru 50 a aikin jarida wanda ya yi zamansa a shekarar 1989-1996 a matsayin babban wakilin fadar White House ta ABC, ya ce a yau manema labarai na nuna "matsanancin hali" a dakin tattaunawa saboda cin mutuncin da suke yi wa Trump.
Saboda yadda suka mayar da hankalin Trump, ya ce a wannan makon a shirin Fox na Tucker Carlson Tonight, 'yan jarida suna yin watsi da tattara labaran siyasa.
"Ba wasan gotcha ba ne kawai," Hume ya ce game da manufar 'yan jarida.
"Ba wai kawai kokarin kunyatar da wani jami'in jama'a ba ne, don fitar da bayanai ne."
Wuraren shakatawa na shakatawa da aka gani dauke da makamai da wukake, masu sukurori da kuma CHAINSAW a matsayin 'yan fashi suna ba su makamai don lalata motoci'
The primates a Knowsley safari shakatawa, Merseyside, an dade da sani su pounce a kan duk wanda ya dakatar da a cikin yadi da kuma ripping kashe wani windscreen wiper ko madubi.
Baboons sun kasance dauke da makamai da wuka, masu sukurori har ma da sarkakiya a wurin shakatawa na Knowsley, Merseyside.
Ma'aikata suna tsoron 'yan wasan kwaikwayo suna ba da makamai masu ban sha'awa, wadanda aka san su da yin watsi da duk wanda ya dakatar da shi kuma ya cire kayan shafawa da madubai.
Yanzu ma'aikata suna tsoron cewa suna dauke da makamai masu kisa "don dariya" da baƙi suka yi don ƙarfafa hare-haren da suke kaiwa, har ma an ga afkawa a kusa da akwatunan kayan aiki da kansu.
Wani ma'aikacin wurin shakatawa ya shaida wa jaridar The Sunday Times cewa: "Ba mu da tabbacin ko wasu daga cikin baƙin da ke son ganin sun kai wa motoci hari, ko kuma sun kama su ne daga manyan motoci da motocin daukar kaya."
"A zahiri za su shiga cikin akwatunan kayan aiki na mutane kuma su dauke su. An ga daya daga cikin magungunan cutar yana tafiya a kusa da wata motsa jiki."
Wani ma'aikacin ya ce: "An same su da wuka da kuma masu sukurori, ina mamakin ko wasu daga cikin baƙin ne suke mika su."
Kuma hare-haren da ake kaiwa a yankunan da ke arewa maso yammacin Ingila ba makawa ne cewa injiniyoyi a arewa maso yammacin Ingila sun san abin da ke faruwa sosai.
Wani injiniya a Sale, Greater Manchester ya ce mutane sun san abin da za su yi tsammani a wurin shakatawa kuma ya sami kwastomomi biyu da suka kamu da cutar a wannan shekarar.
Sun kara da cewa minti daya yara suna son dodanni a motar kuma na gaba ba su da farantin rajista - amma batun ya samar da "kudi mai kyau" ga garejin.
Knowsley ya sake buɗewa a ranar 15 ga Yuni tare da matakan tsaro na Covid-19 bayan da ya nace cewa yana da aminci kamar yadda McDonald ya yi tafiya yayin da baƙi ba sa barin motarsu a tafiyar kilomita biyar.
Gidan shakatawa mai girma 550, da ke dauke da zakuna, damisa, rhinos, bawa da raƙuma, ya yi watsi da rahotannin afuwa mai dauke da makamai a matsayin tatsuniyoyi na birane.
Wani mai magana da yawunsa ya ce: "Mun yi imanin cewa da yawa daga cikin wadannan labaran sun karu da wuce gona da iri yayin da aka sake maimaita su, tare da yin kwalliya don sanya abubuwan da a wasu lokuta ake samu a cikin gidan su zama masu ban sha'awa da kuma rashin yarda."
A shekarar 2012 kamfanin kera motoci kirar Hyundai ya bar dodanni 40 daga wurin shakatawa a kan samfurinsa na New Generation i30 na tsawon awanni 10 don tabbatar da cewa yana da karfin gwiwa ga iyalai da ke da kananan yara.
Kudlow ya ce lissafin cutar coronavirus na gaba zai hada da karin bincike, tsawaita dokar hana fita
Mai ba da shawara kan harkokin tattalin arziki na Fadar White House Larry Kudlow ya yi alkawari a ranar Lahadi cewa gwamnatin tarayya za ta tsawaita dokar hana fita tare da aika wani zagaye na bincike a matsayin wani bangare na kunshin cutar coronavirus mai zuwa.
Kalaman na Kudlow na zuwa ne bayan mako guda da fadar White House ta yi fatan rage harajin albashi daga Majalisa.
"Akwai rajistan $1,200 yana zuwa. Wannan zai zama wani ɓangare na sabon kunshin. Da na fi son a yanke harajin albashi, a saman wannan rajistan," Kudlow ya ce a CNN ta "State of the Union."
"Amma, kamar yadda ya kamata, a siyasa, ba ya aiki."
Duk da cewa ba a sanar da wata yarjejeniya a hukumance ba, Sakataren Baitulmalin Steve Mnuchin da shugaban ma'aikatan fadar White House Mark Meadows sun kasance a Capitol Hill kwanan nan don tattauna cikakkun bayanai game da sabon kayan agaji tare da shugabannin majalisa.
Bayan kawo karshen karin dala 600 na rashin aikin yi da gwamnatin tarayya ke bayarwa, Kudlow ya yi zargin cewa karin kudin na cutar da kananan kamfanoni daga hayar ma'aikata.
"Mun samu ambaliyar tambayoyi da kiran waya da kuma korafe-korafen cewa kananan shaguna da kasuwanci, gidajen cin abinci ba za su iya dawo da hayar mutane ba," in ji shi.
"Sun yi nisa sosai, watakila a watan Maris da ya gabata, hakan ya zama dole, amma, hakika, akwai sakamakon da mutane ba sa komawa bakin aiki."
Mnuchin a farkon wannan rana a "Fox News Sunday" ya fadi hakan a fili cewa: "Ina tsammanin ma'aikata da Amurkawa sun fahimci manufar cewa bai kamata a biya ku kudin da za ku ci gaba da zama a gida ba fiye da aiki ba."
Mnuchin ya ce sabuwar dokar za ta samar da ƙarin amfanin marasa aikin yi, amma ya lura cewa za ta kasance ƙasa da biyan kuɗin da aka bayar a ƙarƙashin Dokar CARES.
Ya ce wasu ma'aikata suna tattara fiye da yadda suka samu a aikin.
Sakamakon haka, a lokacin da aka sake bude harkokin kasuwanci wasu ma'aikata ba su da wani dalili na komawa bakin aiki.
Sakataren ya ce gwamnatin Trump da 'yan Republican Majalisar Dattijai suna kan wannan shafi tare da kunshin dala tiriliyan 1, amma ya lura cewa don sha'awar zartar da doka cikin sauri, za a iya tsayar da batutuwan da suka fi wahalar tattaunawa da 'yan jam'iyyar Democrats don wata doka.
An Kama Mutumin Da Ake Zarginsa Da Kashe Ɗan'uwan Barasa A Greater Noida: 'Yan sanda
An kama wani mutum dan shekara 37 a ranar Lahadi saboda zargin kashe ɗan'uwansa, wanda aka gano gawarsa a wani wuri da aka ware a makon da ya gabata, a Uttar Pradesh's Greater Noida, in ji 'yan sanda.
Wanda ake zargi ya shaida wa 'yan sanda cewa shan giya da kuma mummunan hali da ɗan'uwansa ya yi da mata 'yan iyalinsu na hadin gwiwa, wanda hakan ya kai shi ga aikata laifin, a cewar jami'ai.
An tsinci gawar Bhisham Singh, mazaunin kauyen Bisrakh a Greater Noida, a kusa da daji a wani kebabben wuri kusan mako guda da ya wuce.
Wani kakakin 'yan sanda ya ce, gawar ta haifi alamomi kuma an kwashe wata FIR a ofishin 'yan sanda na Bisrakh kuma an gudanar da bincike.
"A lokacin binciken, shaidu sun kai 'yan sanda ga mutumin, wanda ya mutu, ɗan'uwansa Deepak kuma an tambaye shi. A lokacin da aka tambaye shi, Deepak ya yi ikirarin cewa ya kashe ɗan'uwansa. Ya gaya wa 'yan sanda cewa Bhisham zai ci giya akai-akai, ya haifar da ruckus a gida kuma ya yi kuskure da 'yan uwa mata saboda haka ya yanke shawarar kashe ɗan'uwansa", in ji kakakin.
An kama wanda ake zargi kuma an tuhume shi da laifin kisan kai da sauran tuhume-tuhume masu nasaba da hakan, in ji 'yan sanda.
Dutse daga duniyar Mars ya nufi gida bayan ya cika shekaru 600,000 a Duniya
A karamin dutse za a jefa a cikin sararin samaniya a wannan makon a daya daga cikin mafi ban mamaki interplanetary tafiye-tafiye taba yunkurin.
Za a kaddamar da wani dan karamin basalt na Martian mai girman tsabar kudin 10p a cikin wani bincike na robot na Amurka a ranar Alhamis da kuma motsawa zuwa ga duniya mai launin fata a wata tafiya na watanni bakwai zuwa duniyarsa.
Wannan tashin hankali na ban mamaki, wanda ya yi daidai da tura garwashin zuwa Newcastle, zai zama wani bangare mai mahimmanci na balaguro na Nasa mai zuwa a duniyar Mars 2020.
Injiniyoyin sararin samaniya sun ce dutsen - wanda gidan adana kayan tarihi na Natural History da ke London ya bayar - za a yi amfani da shi wajen daidaita masu bincike a cikin jirgin na'urar robot rover Perseverance bayan da ya sauka kuma ya fara neman alamun rayuwar da ta wuce a duniya.
Wasu daga cikin meteorites na Martian da muke da su ba su da kyau, amma mun zabi wannan musamman saboda yana da wuya kamar tsofaffin takalma
"Lokacin da ka kunna kayan kida kuma ka fara kunna su kafin ka yi amfani da su don bincike, sai ka daidaita su a kan kayan da za su zama kamar abubuwan da ba a san su ba da za ka yi nazarin su. To, me ya fi kyau a yi nazarin duwatsu a duniyar Mars fiye da wanda ya samo asali a wurin?" in ji Farfesa Caroline Smith, mai kula da kayan tarihi na Meteorite.
Masana kimiyya sun yi amannar cewa dutsen da suke komawa duniyar Mars ya samo asali ne daga doron kasa, in ji Smith, wanda shi ma mamba ne a kungiyar kimiyya ta duniyar Mars 2020.
"Kananan kumfa na gas da aka kama a cikin wannan meteorite suna da daidai da yanayin duniyar Mars, don haka mun san dutsenmu ya fito daga wurin."
Ana kyautata zaton cewa an halicci sararin samaniya ne a lokacin da wani dan kunar-bakin-wake ko tauraro ya kutsa cikin duniyar kimanin shekaru 600,000 zuwa 700,000 da suka wuce, inda ya fesa tarkace zuwa sararin samaniya.
Daya daga cikin wadannan gine-gine ya fadi a fadin hasken rana kuma daga baya ya fadi zuwa duniya.
Wannan meteorite - wanda a yanzu ake kira SAU 008 - an gano shi ne a Oman a shekarar 1999 kuma yana kula da gidan adana kayan tarihi na dabi'ar halitta tun daga wannan lokacin.
Daga cikin kayan da suka dace da na'urar Perseverance rover akwai na'urar daukar hoto mai suna Sherloc, wacce za a yi amfani da ita wajen fassara sinadaran da ke cikin duwatsu da kuma tantance ko za su iya dauke da kwayoyin halitta da ke nuna cewa rayuwa ta wanzu - ko kuma ta wanzu - a duniyar Mars.
Haɗa wani yanki na SAU 008 an yi shi ne don tabbatar da cewa an yi hakan tare da iyakar daidaito.
"Dutsen da muke aikawa an zabi shi ne musamman saboda abu ne da ya dace a fannin ilimin sunadarai, amma kuma dutse ne mai matukar wahala," in ji Smith.
"Wasu daga cikin meteorites na Martian da muke da su suna da karfi sosai, wannan meteorite yana da wuya kamar tsofaffin takalma."
Da zarar Perseverance ta zabi duwatsu mafi alfanu da za ta iya samu, za ta zuba su a cikin tsabar kudi a saman Martian.
Wadannan za a dawo da su ta hanyar ayyukan robot na gaba kuma a busa su cikin sararin samaniya zuwa Duniya don bincike.
Barcelona 'suna da dukkanin bangarorin da za su sayar' a wannan bazara kamar yadda Coutinho, Dembele, Rakitic da Vidal suka lissafa don canja wurin
BARCELONA za a san shi a matsayin kulob din da ake sayarwa a wannan bazara, a cewar rahotanni.
Babu kasa da taurari 12 na farko da aka canjawa jerin sunayen 'yan wasan La Liga, da'awar Marca.
Barcelona ta bayar da rahoton cewa Philippe Coutinho ya canja sheka
Kuma wadanda suka hada da 'yan wasan gasar Premier Philippe Coutinho da Ousmane Dembele da Ivan Rakitic da kuma Samuel Umtiti.
