Mutane 200 da suka kashe gobara sun mayar da martani ga cinnawa Karen wuta a kwarin Jurupa - CBS Los Angeles
JURUPA VALLEY (CBSLA) - Wata gobara daji ta tashi a ranar Asabar da yamma a kwarin Jurupa, lamarin da ya kai ga mayar da martani ga masu kashe gobara sama da 200.
An bayar da rahoton gobarar ta Karen ne bayan karfe 3 na yamma a kan titin Sierra Avenue da Karen Lane.
Wutar ta karu ne daga kimanin eka 5-10 zuwa wajen eka 250 tun daga karfe 8 na yamma.
A karshe binciken ya kasance a 50% da kuma 225 kashe gobara daga Cal Fire, Riverside County Fire Department, City of Corona Fire Department, da kuma San Bernardino County gobara sun kasance a wurin fama da wuta.
An dakatar da ci gaba a kan wutar amma ana sa ran albarkatun za su ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin dare don lura da yanayin.
