Wasu kwangilolin suna da maganganun da ke ba su damar rage karancin lamunin idan yawan mutanen da ke wani yanki ya ragu da wani kaso, amma ba a sani ba ko wannan yanayin yana cikin kowane irin kwangilar da ke tsakanin kamfanonin tallafin da masu gidajen su.
A lokaci guda, kamfanonin suna ba da rangwame mai yawa ga masu tallace-tallace don cika wuraren da ake da su a kan allon talla da kuma ba su kudi mafi daraja.
Gidajen tallace-tallace a Sydney CBD da kuma unguwannin waje waɗanda yawanci ke karɓar tallace-tallace guda shida suna fama don cika dukkanin wuraren da ake da su.
Amma an kyautata wasu shafuka - kamar su allon tallace-tallace na kafofin watsa labarai na mita 40 x 10 a filin jirgin saman Sydney.
OOh! 'Yan jarida sun ki yin tsokaci, amma a wani taro da suka yi a Macquarie Australia a watan Mayu, sun ba da tutar fiye da dala miliyan 20 na ajiyar kuɗin haya.
JC Decaux ya ki yin sharhi.
Filayen jiragen sama da zirga-zirgar jama'a kwangilar tallace-tallace ne na kamfanonin talla.
A cewar rahoton kungiyar 'yan jarida na waje na shekarar 2019, kudaden shiga daga sufuri - ciki har da filayen jiragen sama - ya kai dala miliyan 169.4 yayin da kudaden shiga daga kayan titi da waje na motocin bas da motoci ya kai dala miliyan 266.5.
Kasuwancin JC Decaux yana da kwangila tare da filin jirgin saman Sydney, Yarra Trams, filin jirgin saman Perth da kuma Sydney Buses. OOh! Media yana da allon tallace-tallace a wurare kamar wuraren shakatawa na Qantas, a wajen filin jirgin sama na Sydney, filin jirgin saman Adelaide, filin jirgin saman Darwin da kuma tashoshin jirgin kasa a Sydney da Melbourne.
An yi awon gaba da filin jirgin saman Melbourne da jiragen kasa na Sydney a lokacin annobar kuma ba a yanke hukunci a hukumance ba.
Melbourne ita ce kwangila ta biyu mafi girma a filin jirgin sama a Australiya kuma riga-kafin cutar coronavirus ya kai miliyoyin miliyoyi a kowace shekara.
A sakamako na cikakken shekara a watan Fabrairu, oOh! Media ya ce ya samar da dala miliyan 65.9 daga nau'in 'fly' wanda yawanci ya kunshi kudaden shiga daga filin jirgin saman Sydney.
Kudaden da aka samu daga 'commute', wanda ya ƙunshi kwangilar layin dogo da kayan titi da Adshel ya mallaka a baya kafin a saye shi ta hanyar oOh!, ya kai dala miliyan 234.8.
JC Decaux Australia ta samu kudin shiga dala miliyan 37.7 daga sufuri a shekarar 2018, bisa ga sakamakon kudi na shekarar 2018 da ta shigar ga Hukumar Kasuwanci da Zuba Jari ta Australiya.
To amma dukkanin wadannan adadi za su iya raguwa sosai a wannan shekarar.
Alkaluman jaridar Standard Media Index, wadanda suka bayar da rahoton kashe kudade hudu daga cikin manyan kungiyoyin talla biyar, sun ce kasuwar tallace-tallace ta waje ta karu da kashi 68 cikin 100 a watan Yuni.
Ta hanyar kwatanta, sakamakon wucin gadi na watan Yuni ya nuna cewa kashe kuɗi na dijital ya ragu kashi 37 cikin dari, yayin da rediyo na birni ya fadi kashi 48 cikin dari.
Gidan talabijin na birni ya fadi kashi 34 cikin 100 a watan Yuni, yawan kuɗin jarida ya ragu da kashi 49 cikin 100 kuma yawan kuɗin da ake kashewa a mujallu ya ragu kashi 66 cikin 100.
Leicester na farin cikin samun gurbi a gasar kwallon kafa ta Turai in ji Jamie Vardy wanda ya lashe gasar Golden Boot
Jamie Vardy ya yarda da rashin jin dadinsa na rashin samun gurbi a gasar kwallon kafa ta Champions League, amma ya ce Leicester City ta cimma burinsu na farkon kakar wasanni na neman cancantar shiga gasar Turai.
Foxes sun kasance na biyu a watan Disamba kuma na uku a lokacin da aka sake fara kwallon kafa bayan kullewa, amma sun dauki maki hudu ne kawai daga wasanni biyar da suka gabata don kammalawa na biyar a gasar ta Premier.
Nasarar da aka yi a ranar karshe a kan Manchester United za ta kai wasan daf da na kusa da na karshe, amma kungiyar Brendan Rodgers ta yi rashin nasara da ci 2-0, abin da Vardy ya ce shi ne abin da ya fi tayar da hankali.
"Ya kasance abin baƙin ciki, mafi yadda muka ƙare har rasa wasan," ya ce a kan Sky Sports a cikakken lokaci.
"Amma mun ce a dakin miya, mun yi niyya a bayan kofofin da aka rufe don mu cancanci zuwa Turai kuma mun yi hakan."
"Mun samu damar shiga gasar zakarun Turai kuma hakan ya fi kyau, amma za mu yi tunani a kan hakan kuma mu dawo da karfi a shekara mai zuwa."
"Yana da wuya a dauka, amma babban burinmu shi ne Turai kuma mun sami nasarar hakan."
Yayin da kungiyarsa ta yi kasa a gwiwa, Vardy da kansa ya kawo karshen kakar wasa ta bana a matsayin dan wasan da ke kan gaba a gasar ta Premier yana dan shekara 33, inda ya ci kwallo sau 23.
Ya jinjina wa abokan wasan kungiyarsa wajen karbar kyautar, ya kuma ce har yanzu akwai nisan mil da yawa a cikinsa a matakin sama, duk da cewa shekarunsa na cigaba.
"Na yi farin ciki, duk game da kungiyar ne, da ban kasance a matsayin da nake da shi ba tare da su ba, kuma na ajiye wasu 'yan kaɗan."
"Zan ɗan huta yanzu kuma in dawo kakar wasa mai zuwa a shirye in tafi. Abin farin cikin shi ne cewa ba na jin shekarata, ƙafafuna suna da kyau kuma suna taɓa itace ba na ɗaukar rauni da yawa, don haka ya kamata in ci gaba da kasancewa a kan hakan kuma in dawo da karfi kamar yadda zan iya a shekara mai zuwa."
Coronavirus: Matafiya daga Spain sun ce a killace su
Matafiya da suka isa Burtaniya daga Spain dole ne a killace su na tsawon kwanaki 14, a karkashin sabbin dokokin tafiye-tafiye na coronavirus.
An sanar da su a ranar Asabar bayan karuwar wadanda suka kamu da cutar coronavirus a Spain, inda aka samu sabbin mutane sama da 900 da suka kamu da cutar a ranar Juma'a.
Jami'an Mutanen Espanya sun kuma yi gargadin cewa za a iya samun tashin hankali na biyu yayin da manyan birane suka ga karuwar cutar.
Kamfanonin jiragen sama da suka hada da British Airways sun zargi sabbin matakan a matsayin "duk da haka wani abin takaici" ga masu hutun Birtaniya.
Ma'aikatar sufuri ta shawarci mutanen da ke hutu a Spain da su bi dokokin yankin, su koma gida kamar yadda aka saba, kuma su duba shafin yanar gizon kula da tafiye-tafiye na ofishin harkokin waje don ƙarin bayani.
Ofishin Harkokin Wajen yana ba da shawara game da tafiye-tafiye masu mahimmanci zuwa babban yankin Spain, duk da haka matakan kebewa sun shafi waɗanda suka dawo daga babban yankin Spain, da Canary Islands da Balearic Islands, kamar Mallorca da Ibiza.
Shawarwarin ofishin harkokin waje yana da tasiri ga inshorar tafiye-tafiye.
Cikin wadanda sabbin dokokin suka shafa har da Sakataren sufuri Grant Shapps, wanda ya soma hutunsa a kasar Spain a ranar Asabar.
Ana sa ran zai ci gaba da tafiyarsa kamar yadda aka tsara kuma ya ware bisa jagorancin dawowarsa.
An fara gabatar da matakan killace matafiya a Burtaniya a farkon watan Yuni.
Amma bayan matsin lamba daga masana'antun sufurin jiragen sama da tafiye-tafiye, gwamnati da gwamnatocin da suka rage sun wallafa jerin sunayen kasashen da aka kebe daga dokokin.
Kamfanin jiragen sama na British Airways ya ce ya yi "bacin rai" game da sabbin sauye-sauye ga shawarwari da ka'idojin tafiye-tafiye na gwamnati, duk da cewa kamfanin jirgin ya ce jiragensa na ci gaba da aiki.
Ya ce wannan mataki shi ne "ya jefa dubban tsare-tsaren tafiye-tafiye na Britaniya cikin rikice-rikice."
Kungiyar masu kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama ta ce sabbin matakan za su ci gaba da lalata abin da ya riga ya zama wani gagarumin sake farawa a fannin sufurin jiragen sama wanda ke ci gaba da fuskantar babbar kalubale a tarihinsa.
Babban kamfanin yawon shakatawa na Birtaniya, Tui, ya soke jiragensa saboda tashi zuwa babban yankin Spain da tsibirin Canary a ranar Lahadi.
Abokan ciniki a halin yanzu suna hutu za su iya dawowa a cikin jirgin da suka yi niyyar komawa gida.
Duk da haka, kamfanin jirgin sama na kasafin kudi EasyJet ya ce "abin baƙin ciki ne" kuma zai yi aiki da cikakken jadawalin a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
"Abokan ciniki da ba sa so su yi tafiye-tafiye za su iya canja wurin jiragen su ba tare da kudin canji ba ko kuma su karbi takardar shaidar darajar ajiyar," in ji kamfanin a cikin wata sanarwa.
Mai magana da yawun kungiyar jami'an kula da tafiye-tafiye na Birtaniya (Abta) ya ce canjin dokar killacewa ta gwamnati "abin baƙin ciki ne."
"Muna ba da shawarar gwamnati ta yi la'akari da cire ka'idojin killace jiragen da ke zuwa da kuma daga wasu yankuna da ke da karancin kamuwa da cutar, ko kuma zuwa wurare kamar tsibirin Balearic ko Canaries - waɗanda suka bambanta da babban yankin Spain - don kauce wa ƙarin lalacewar masana'antun yawon shakatawa na Burtaniya da ke shigowa da waje", in ji shi.
Ya zuwa yanzu kasar Spain ta samu mutuwar mutane sama da 28,000 da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus.
A ranar Alhamis, ta ga karuwar masu kamuwa da cutar a kowace rana tun lokacin da aka kawo karshen kullewarta.
Yankin na Catalonia ya zama wani yanki na baya-bayan nan da ya yi fama da tashe-tashen hankula.
Yankin arewa maso gabas mai arziki, wanda ke da gida a Barcelona, ya ba da umarnin rufe dukkanin wuraren shakatawa na tsawon makonni biyu tare da sanya dokar hana fita ta tsakar dare a mashaya a yankin Barcelona mai girma.
Guy Hedgecoe na BBC a Madrid ya ce yaduwar cutar a tsakanin matasa wani abin damuwa ne musamman yadda suke taruwa da yawa a birane da daddare.
Faransa ta gargadi 'yan kasarta da kada su yi balaguro zuwa Catalonia yayin da Norway ta ce za ta fara killace mutanen da ke zuwa daga Spain.
Gwamnati ta bukaci ma'aikata da su "fahimci wadanda suka dawo daga Spain wadanda yanzu za su bukaci su kebe kansu."
Amma sakataren gidauniyar Labour Nick Thomas-Symonds ya yi kira ga gwamnati da ta yi cikakken bayani kan yadda za ta tallafawa wadanda abin ya shafa, inda ya kara da cewa labarin zai kasance "na matukar damuwa ga iyalan da suka kama a Spain ko kuma suke shirin tafiye-tafiye."
Ministan farko na Scotland Nicola Sturgeon ya bayyana cewa an yanke wannan shawarar ne bayan da aka yi nazarin bayanan baya-bayan nan a ranar Asabar.
"Hakan ya ƙarfafa batun cewa waɗannan al'amura suna fuskantar sauye-sauye a takaice don haka shawarata ita ce in yi taka tsantsan game da tafiye-tafiye da ba su da muhimmanci a ƙasashen waje", in ji ta.
John Blackmore, daga Hampshire, saboda ya tashi zuwa iyalinsa a Spain tare da matarsa da kuma kananan yara biyu.
Amma sabbin dokokin na nufin dole ne ya soke, saboda tsoron cewa ma'aikaciyar matarsa ba za ta iya saukar da ita ba ta dauki karin makonni biyu don killacewa a lokacin da suka dawo.
Ya ce yana ganin ba zai yiwu su samu kudin fansar jirgin ba, saboda ba a soke shi ba.
"Na fatattake ni," ya shaida wa BBC.
"Ina da iyali a Spain waɗanda ba su ga jikokinsu kaɗai ba tun lokacin Kirsimeti."
Lois Stothard, daga Kudancin Yorkshire, ta shaida wa BBC cewa ta shirya hutun zuwa Sevilla a matsayin abin mamaki don ranar haihuwar saurayinta na 30 - saboda tashi daga ranar Lahadi da safe - amma yanzu tana jin cewa ba za ta iya tafiya ba.
"Ni ma'aikaciya ce - ni malama ce - kuma saurayina yana da sadaukarwar aiki don haka ba za mu iya killace kanmu na tsawon kwanaki 14 ba idan muka dawo," in ji ta.
"Ba za mu iya dawo da kuɗi ba kuma mu canza kamfanin yana so ya ninka abin da na riga na biya a cikin kudade.
Ina matukar baƙin ciki da damuwa yayin da muke cike da shirye-shiryen tafiya."
Ted Cruz ya ce manufofin Pelosi su ne "tatsar da tsabar kudi kan matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka"
Washington - Sanata Ted Cruz dan jam'iyyar Republican na Texas ya zargi kakakin majalisa Nancy Pelosi da 'yan jam'iyyar Democrats da tura wani kunshin kayan agaji na coronavirus wanda ya mayar da hankali kan "tatsar da tsabar kudi kan matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka" yayin da ake ci gaba da tattaunawa kan mataki na gaba.
A wata hira da ya yi da "Face the Nation" a ranar Lahadi, Cruz ya ce kasar na fuskantar rikice-rikice guda biyu a lokaci guda: annobar cutar da ta lakume rayukan mutane sama da 600,000 a duniya da kuma "hadarin tattalin arziki" a Amurka.
Amma Cruz ya ce Pelosi, wanda ya fito a kan "Face the Nation" a gaban sanata, "ba ya mai da hankali kan ko wanene ba."
"Manufofinta na girgiza tsabar kudi a matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka," in ji Texas Republican.
"Kuma musamman, ka kalli takardar kudi ta dala tiriliyan 3 da ta ke kokarin turawa, kawai tana tura wa kawayenta kudi ne ba tare da magance matsalar ba a zahiri. Manufarmu ita ce Amurkawa suna son komawa bakin aiki. Suna so su iya samar da iyalinsu."
'Yan Majalisar Republican da Fadar White House sun kwashe makon jiya suna tattaunawa kan sharuddan kashi na hudu na martanin coronavirus, wanda suke sa ran za su kashe dala tiriliyan 1.
A karshen mako, shugaban ma'aikatan fadar White House Mark Meadows da Sakataren Baitul Steven Mnuchin sun koma Capitol Hill don ƙarin tattaunawa da ma'aikatan majalisar dattijai, kuma Mnuchin ya fada wa Fox News a wata hira da aka yi a ranar Lahadi, an bayyana cikakkun bayanai daga Shugaban Majalisar Dattijai, Mitch McConnell a ranar Litinin.
Batun da ya fi daukar hankali ga 'yan majalisar dokoki - kuma wani batu na jayayya tsakanin 'yan Republican da 'yan Democrats - shi ne karewar karin albashi na rashin aikin yi, wanda ya fara gudana a wannan karshen mako.
Yayin da 'yan jam'iyyar Democrats ke son kunshin coronavirus na "lokaci na hudu" don kiyaye karuwar dala 600 ga amfanin, 'yan Republican suna kiran a dawo da shi tare da jayayya da cewa wasu Amurkawa sun fi samun karfi daga rashin aikin yi fiye da yadda suka yi a albashi.
Cruz ya ce fiye da rabin Amurkawa da ke karbar kyaututtukan rashin aikin yi ana biyan su fiye da lokacin da suke aiki kuma ya ce yana tattaunawa da kananan 'yan kasuwa a Texas wadanda ke fuskantar matsala wajen sake ma'aikata.
"Tabbas, ba za su dawo ba saboda gwamnatin tarayya tana biyan su, a wasu lokuta, sau biyu na kudin da za su zauna a gida," in ji shi.
Cruz ya ce kamata ya yi Majalisa ta mayar da hankali kan zartar da wata doka ta farfadowa da za ta sa Amurkawa su koma bakin aiki ta hanyar sassauta haraji da ka'idoji kan kananan kamfanoni: "maimakon kawai kawar da tiriliyan daga kofa, takardar dawo da kudin zai dakatar da harajin albashi, wanda zai ba da albashi ga duk wanda ke aiki a Amurka. Hakan ya sa mutane su koma aiki", in ji shi.
A makon da ya gabata ne shugaba Trump ya bukaci kunshin taimako na gaba da ya hada da yanke harajin albashi, amma Mnuchin ya ce ba zai kasance cikin dokar ba, saboda an samu karbuwa a tsakanin 'yan Republican.
Mista Trump ya yarda cewa yanke harajin albashi zai kasance ba tare da doka ta gaba ba amma ya nemi ya dora laifin kan 'yan jam'iyyar Democrats.
Cruz, wanda a makon da ya gabata ya ki amincewa da kudin kunshin na gaba, ya ce a ranar Lahadi ba ya cikin jirgin tare da matakin daga 'yan'uwansa 'yan Republican.
Amma kuma ya soki lissafin dala tiriliyan 3 da 'yan majalisar da ke rike da madafun iko na jam'iyyar Democrat suka zartar a watan Mayu, ya kuma zargi abokan hamayyarsa na siyasa da cewa da gangan suka kirkiro wani mataki na damfarar shugaban kasa gabanin zaben watan Nuwamba.
"Maƙasudin da 'yan jam'iyyar Democrats ke da shi kawai shi ne su yi nasara a kan Donald Trump, kuma sun yanke shawarar hanyar da ta fi dacewa wajen kayar da Donald Trump ita ce rufe duk wata kasuwanci a Amurka, rufe kowace makaranta a Amurka," in ji shi.
"Kun sani, Nancy Pelosi ta yi magana kan maza da mata masu aiki. Abin da ta ke gabatarwa shi ne hana maza da mata masu aiki daga aiki."
Rahul Gandhi Ya Jefi Mutane Kan Batun Rajasthan
Rahul Gandhi na majalisa ya wallafa wani bidiyo a yau yana ƙoƙarin yaɗa jama'a a kan jam'iyyar BJP kan abubuwan da suka faru a Rajasthan.
Amfani da hashtag #SpeakUpForDemocracy, sakonsa na Hindia ya bukaci jama'a da su "haɗa kai da kuma ɗaga muryarmu ga dimokuradiyya."
Majalisa na shirin gudanar da zanga-zanga a karkara a ranar Litinin kan halin da ake ciki a Rajasthan, inda gwamnatin Ashok Gehlot ke fama da tsira.
Yayin da jam'iyyar ta ce za a gudanar da zanga-zanga a wajen Rashtrapati Bhavan, mazaunin shugaban kasa Ram Nath Kovind.
A cikin bidiyon, Majalisa ta zargi BJP da "karkatar da kundin tsarin mulki da kuma rushe dimokuradiyya" yayin da kasar baki daya ke yaki da cutar coronavirus.
Haka ya yi a Madhya Pradesh, in ji Majalisa.
"Mun bukaci nan da nan a gudanar da zaman majalisa wanda ke cikin hakkokinmu na tsarin mulki," in ji jam'iyyar a cikin bidiyon.
Gwamnan Rajasthan Kalraj Mishra ya karyata shawarar daya gabatar na fara zaman majalisa.
An gabatar da na biyu a yau wanda ya ce yana nazari.
Gwamnatin Mr Gehlot ta shiga cikin rikice-rikice mai zurfi bayan da mataimakinsa Sachin Pilot ya mayar da 'yan tawaye tare da wasu 'yan gwagwarmaya da ke goyon bayansa.
Jam'iyyar ba ta iya rabuwa da 'yan tawayen don saukar da alamar mafi yawa a cikin taron.
Mista Pilot - wanda aka kwace mukaminsa a jam'iyyar da kuma gwamnati - ya samu sauƙi na ɗan lokaci daga rashin cancanta daga babbar kotun Rajasthan, wacce ta ce Kakakin ba zai iya ɗaukar mataki ba har sai an yanke hukunci kan babbar tambaya ta tsarin mulki game da ikonsa.
A gobe ne Kotun Koli za ta karbi wannan tambaya, wacce kuma za ta yanke hukuncin ko wata kotu za ta iya tsoma baki cikin hukuncin da Kakakin ya yanke.
Majalisa ce kadai ta wuce alamar mafi rinjaye a taron mai mambobi 200.
Kungiyar Pilot ta yi ikirarin goyon bayan 30 MLAs, amma ya zuwa yanzu, shaidar ta nuna cewa 19 ne kawai.
BJP tana da 72 kuma ciki har da masõya da 'yancin kai, tana tsaye a 97.
Idan kotu ta yanke shawarar goyon bayan Mista Pilot, Majalisa za ta iya rasa na biyu daga cikin gwamnatoci uku da ta kafa a jihohin tsakiyar kasar bayan zaben 'yan majalisa na 2018.
A watan Maris, ta rasa gwamnatin Kamal Nath a Madhya Pradesh bayan da Jyotiraditya Scindia ya koma jam'iyyar BJP tare da 22 daga cikin 'yan majalisarsa.
An kama jami'an 'yan sandan Kenyan bayan harbi mai tsanani a Garissa
An kama jami'an 'yan sanda biyu a Kenya dangane da wani harbi da aka yi inda aka kashe mutane biyu.
Wannan harbi ya faru ne a kasuwar Soko Ng'ombe da ke gabashin gundumar Garissa a ranar Asabar, yayin zanga-zangar nuna adawa da kama wani mutum da ake zargi da kisan kai.
An bayyana sunan wadanda suka mutu a matsayin Aden Abdi Madobe da kuma Muhiyadin Adow Shibin.
'Yan sandan kasar Kenya sun kaddamar da bincike kan harbin.
Zai hada da "binciken bincike" na bindigogi na jami'an.
Garissa MP Aden Duale ya kira mace-macen "mutuwa" kuma ya yi la'akari da " zaluncin 'yan sanda" a cikin wata sanarwa da aka sanya a Facebook.
Masu zanga-zangar sun nuna damuwa game da 'yan sanda a lokacin annobar.
A cewar Amnesty International, jami'an Kenyan sun kashe mutane 21 tun daga watan Maris saboda rashin bin matakan kariya daga cutar Koronabirus kamar dokar hana fita da kuma sanya takunkumin rufe fuska.
A farkon wannan watan 'yan sanda a babban birnin Nairobi sun harba gas mai sa hawaye kuma sun kama masu zanga-zanga da dama da suka shiga zanga-zangar Saba Saba na shekara-shekara - wani zanga-zangar da aka fara shekaru 30 da suka gabata a kan mulkin mallaka na shugaban kasa Daniel arap Moi.
Masu aiko da rahotanni sun ce abin da ya faru a wannan shekarar ya samu karin karfi ne ta hanyar fushi kan hargitsin da 'yan sanda suka yi a lokacin kullewar Covid-19.
Shivraj Singh Chouhan Na Gwajin Covid Mai Kyau
Babban Ministan Madhya Pradesh Shivraj Singh Chouhan, wanda a ranar Asabar ya tabbatar da cewa ya yi gwajin cutar COVID-19, ya yaba a ranar Lahadi da safe don ya ce yana da "kyau" kuma ya yaba wa ma'aikatan gaba-gaba a yakin da ake yi da cutar coronavirus.
Babban Ministan ya kuma maimaita gargadin da ya yi daga jiya, lokacin da ya bukaci mutane da su bi ka'idoji, kamar nisantar jama'a da kuma amfani da takunkumin fuska.
"Ina da kyau, abokaina. sadaukar da kai na mayaƙan coronavirus, waɗanda suka sadaukar da rayukansu cikin haɗari, abin yabo ne. Ina sarautar dukkanin mayaƙan coronavirus na jihar", Mr Chouhan ya aiko da rahoto daga asibitin Chirayu na Bhopal, inda aka shigar da shi a jiya.
"Ku nisan mita biyu, ku wanke hannuwanku akai-akai kuma ku sanya takunkumin fuska - wadannan su ne manyan makaman da muke da su don kauce wa cutar Koronabirus. Ina kira ga dukkan mutane - ku yi amfani da wadannan makamai don kanku da kuma masoyanku", in ji shi.
"Dukkanku ku yi taka tsantsan, ku zauna lafiya lafiya, wannan shi ne abin da nake addu'a ga Allah" Mista Chouhan ya kara da cewa.
A ranar Asabar Mista Chouhan ya bayar da rahoton cewa ya yi gwajin cutar duk da kokarin da ya yi na kauce wa kamuwa da cutar kuma ya yi gargadin cewa "kamar rashin kulawa ne kawai ke gayyatar cutar coronavirus."
Da yake zantawa da manema labarai a safiyar yau Mr Chouhan ya ce duk da barazanar kamuwa da cutar "babu bukatar fargaba" ya kuma bukaci wadanda ke nuna alamun cutar da su yiwa kansu gwaji.
"Idan ka kamu da cutar, babu bukatar ka ji tsoro. Kada ka ɓoye alamun cutar amma ka gaya wa likitoci nan da nan, don haka za a iya fara magani.
Madhya Pradesh na da mutane kusan 27,000 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19, daga cikinsu sama da 7,600 na aiki sannan 799 na mutuwa da ke da nasaba da kwayar cutar.
Indiya ta samu karuwar wadanda suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a cikin makonnin da suka gabata, inda aka gano sabbin kamuwa da cutar sama da 45,000 a kowace rana tun daga ranar 23 ga watan Yuli.
Adadin wadanda aka tabbatar sun kamu da cutar coronavirus ya kusan kai 14 lakh; daga cikin wadannan sama da 4.67 lakh sun kamu da cutar kuma sama da 32,000 sun mutu da ke da alaƙa da kwayar cutar.
Karuwar wadanda suka kamu da cutar, wanda ya yi daidai da sassauta ka'idojin kulle a yankunan da ba su da matsuguni a kasar, ya sa Indiya ta zama ta uku a jerin kasashen da cutar ta fi shafa.
Sai dai Amurka (41.78 wadanda suka kamu da cutar) da Brazil (23.94 wadanda suka kamu da cutar) sun fi muni.
Ministan cikin gida na Tunisiya ya kira sabon PM, da zai kafa gwamnati a cikin wata guda
An nada ministan cikin gida na Tunusiya Hichem Mechichi don kafa gwamnati ta gaba, in ji ofishin shugaban kasar, a tsakiyar tashin hankalin siyasa tsakanin manyan jam'iyyu a arewacin Afirka.
Lauyan mai shekaru 46 ya maye gurbin Elyes Fakhfakh, wanda ya yi murabus a matsayin firayim minista a farkon watan nan.
Amma Mechichi ba ya daga cikin sunayen da jam'iyyun siyasar da ke mulki suka gabatar wa shugaba Kais Saied.
A cikin wata sanarwa bayan sanarwar ranar Asabar, Mechichi ya ce zai "yi aiki don samar da gwamnatin da ta dace da tsammanin dukkanin 'yan Tunisiya."
An yabawa Tunisiya a matsayin wani labari mai wuya na samun nasara ga sauyin mulki na dimokuradiyya bayan tashin hankalin yankin bazara na Larabawa wanda ya haifar da juyin juya halin da ta yi a shekarar 2011.
Amma shugabanninta sun yi kokarin cika tsammanin al'ummar Tunisiya kuma tattalin arzikin da ya riga ya yi kasa a gwiwa sakamakon rufe iyakokin kasar saboda annobar COVID-19.
Cutar ta kashe mutane kusan 50 kuma ta kama sama da 1,400 a Tunisiya.
Tare da kasancewa ministan cikin gida a gwamnatin mai barin gado, Mechichi ya kasance mai bai wa shugaba Saied shawara kan harkokin shari'a.
A baya ya kasance shugaban ma'aikata a ma'aikatar sufuri kuma ya yi aiki a ma'aikatar kula da harkokin jama'a.
Yanzu yana da wata guda da zai kafa gwamnati, wacce a lokacin za ta fuskanci kuri'ar amincewa da majalisar dokoki kuma za ta bukaci cikakken rinjaye don samun nasara.
Idan ba haka ba, za a rushe majalisar kuma za a gudanar da sabon zabe cikin watanni uku.
A zaben da ya gabata da aka yi a watan Oktoba, jam'iyyar Ennahdha ta zo kan gaba amma ta kasa da yawancin mutane kuma daga bisani ta amince ta shiga gwamnatin hadin gwiwa.
Fakhfakh ya yi murabus a ranar 15 ga watan Yuli, bayan kasa da watanni biyar a ofis, ya yi barazanar sake barkewar siyasa a kasar yayin da yake fama da faɗuwar tattalin arziki na annobar.
Murabus din ya zurfafa jayayyar siyasa da Ennahdha kan zargin da ake yi wa Fakhfakh na rikice-rikice na ban sha'awa.
Dangantaka tsakanin shugaban mai shekaru 47 da haihuwa da Ennahdha ta yi tsami tun bayan zaben 'yan majalisar dokoki na watan Oktoba.
Fakhfakh ya sauka a ranar da jam'iyyar ta shigar da karar rashin amincewa da shi.
Tun da farko Ennahdha ya zabi firaminista mai zaman kansa, amma ya kasa samun goyon bayan majalisa, wanda hakan ya sa shugaban kasar ya sanya sunan tsohon ministan kudi Fakhfakh a matsayin mukaddashin.
Fuskantar tsammanin za a gudanar da sabon zabe, daga bisani Ennahdha ya amince ya shiga cikin gwamnatin hadin gwiwa.
Mota na tafiyar da jama'a, mai zanga-zanga ya harbe a Colorado
AURORA, Colo. (AP) - Wata mota ta kutsa cikin taron jama'a kuma an harbi wani mai zanga-zanga a unguwar Denver da ke Aurora a lokacin da ake zanga-zangar adawa da rashin adalcin launin fata.
Ma'aikatar 'yan sanda ta Aurora ta bayyana a Twitter cewa masu zanga-zangar suna tafiya a kan babbar hanyar 225 a ranar Asabar lokacin da wata mota ta ratsa.
'Yan sanda sun ce wani mai zanga-zanga ya harba wani makami, inda ya bugi akalla mutum guda da aka kai shi asibiti cikin yanayi mai karko.
Hukumomi sun ce an tura motar kuma suna bincike.
Masu zanga-zangar sun kuma fasa tagogi zuwa gidan kotu sannan aka soma cinna wuta a wani ofishi, in ji 'yan sanda.
An kaddamar da wani taro ba bisa ka'ida ba kuma 'yan sanda sun umarci masu zanga-zangar da su bar yankin, in ji hukumomi.
An kara samun tashe-tashen hankula a zanga-zangar da aka yi a baya-bayan nan kan rashin adalcin launin fata tun bayan da aka tura jami'an gwamnatin tarayya domin dakile zanga-zanga a Portland, Oregon.
'Yan sanda sun bayyana tashin hankali a Seattle a ranar Asabar.
Zanga-zangar da ta haifar da mutuwar George Floyd a ranar 25 ga watan Mayu, wani bakar fata a Minnesota wanda ya mutu bayan da wani jami'in farar fata ya rike shi a kasa tare da gwiwa a wuyansa, sun kuma nuna wasu lokuta na mummunan tashin hankali na 'yan sanda.
A jihar Colorado, masu zanga-zanga sun ja hankali kan mutuwar Elijah McClain, wanda 'yan sanda suka dakatar da shi a lokacin da yake tafiya a kan titin Aurora a watan Agusta na shekarar 2019 bayan da wani mai kira 911 ya ba da rahoton cewa yana da zargi.
'Yan sanda sun ajiye shi a wani wurin shakatawa, kuma ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya sun ba da gudummawar ketamine mai nauyin mil 500, don kwantar da hankalinsa.
Ya shiga bugun zuciya, daga baya aka bayyana cewa kwakwalwa ta mutu kuma aka cire shi daga tallafin rayuwa.
Canjin yanayi ya gurbata tafkin Tahoe da ya shahara a bayyane
South Lake Tahoe, California - Duk da annobar, har a ranar mako guda, har yanzu mutane suna cunkoso a bakin tekun Paparoma a tafkin Tahoe.
"Ina son yin zango da hawa keke da kuma yin iyo a tafkin," in ji wata yarinya mai suna Dakota.
"Wannan wani kyakkyawan abu ne da kowa ke son ziyarta," a cewar Emerica Benitas.
Wannan shi ne dalilin da ya sa harkokin kasuwancin ruwa na Matt Meunier ke ci gaba da karfi, har ma a cikin annoba.
Ya ce yana ganin "abin ban mamaki. Tafkin Tahoe shi ne tafki mafi tsabta, mafi ban mamaki, ina tsammanin, a kasar nan."
Yanzu mummunan labari: Tafkin Tahoe ba shi da tsabta, ba a bayyane ba, kamar yadda ya kasance a lokacin da ya koma nan sama da shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
"Abin da muke lura da shi da yawa ya sauka a kan duwatsu," in ji Meunier.
"Kana samun wannan algae mai ban mamaki a kan duwatsu."
Canjin yanayi, masana kimiyya sun yi imanin cewa, ya shafi zafin ruwa da haka, haske.
Kuma mutane miliyan 15 ne ke ziyartar tafkin a duk shekara - tare da shara da suke fita.
Meunier ya ce tafiye-tafiye na ruwa don tsabtace kasan tafkin ya sami tsohuwar shara.
"Kuma idan na ce tsohon shara, ina nufin '60s, '70s," in ji Meunier.
"Gwani na giya, gwangwani na soda, gwangwani na coci daga zamanin dā."
Masana kimiyya suna lura da tsabtace tafkin Tahoe a kowace shekara ta hanyar sauke farin faifai, sannan su auna yadda za su iya ganin sa.
Farfesa Geoff Schladow na UC Davis ya ce "muhimmin alama ce ta yadda tafkin yake da lafiya."
Lokacin da aka auna shi a shekarar da ta gabata, tsabtace tafkin ya kai kimanin kafa 80.
Wannan yana nufin za ka iya ganin cewa Disc 80 feet saukar.
Amma, ka yi la'akari da wannan, kimanin shekaru 20 da suka wuce, tsabtace tafkin ya kai kafa 100.
Wannan shine yanayin da masana kimiyya ke kokarin juyawa.
Amma suna yaki da tasirin sauyin yanayi, ci gaban da ke kewaye da tafkin da kuma wani abu da aka kara a tafkin a shekarun 1960: Kananan jatan lande masu cutarwa da aka shigo da su don ciyar da kifin.
Bai yi aiki ba.
"Da zarar jatan lande ya shigo, ba zato ba tsammani babu masu tsabta a cikin tafkin," in ji Schladow.
Irin wadannan kalubale na fuskantar tafkuna da jikin ruwa a fadin duniya.
"Darasi a nan shi ne, idan ba za ka iya yi a Tahoe ba, to, wane fata ne ake da shi ga dukkanin koguna da bakin teku, da koguna da tafkuna a fadin kasar da ba za su taba samun irin wannan kulawa ba, da irin wadannan albarkatu?" in ji Schladow.
Meunier ya ce yana da "fatan alheri" saboda "idan akwai ruwan azurfa na annobarmu, ina tsammanin hakan ya nuna cewa yanayi zai dawo kuma ya warkar da kansa idan kawai muka sauƙaƙa wannan matsin lamba, wannan matsin lamba na dan adam, daga ciki kuma muka bar hakan ya faru. Akwai hujjoji a yanzu".
